\id ROM
\h Irumaniyyen 
\toc1 Irumaniyyen 
\toc2 Irumaniyyen 
\toc3 Rum. 
\mt1 Irumaniyyen  
\c 1
\s1 Tamezwarut  
\m
\v 1 Bulus, amsexxar n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \add rrasul\add* ittwařaɣan d ittwasekken, ittwaḥuzen i L’Injil n AREBBI \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Řex. 9:15; 13:2; Gal. 1:15. \x*  
\v 2 - \add L’Injil\add* nni izzar iwaɛd zzayes zeg umewaru s inabiyyen nnes di Tira Iqeddsen - \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Amz. 3:15; 22:18; 26:4; 49:10; Aɛwd. 18:15; 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:11; Ica. 4:2; 7:14; 9:5; 40:10; Irm. 23:5; 33:14; Ḥiz. 34:23; 37:24; Dan. 9:24; Mixa 7:20. \x*  
\v 3 x Mmis, wenni dd-ittwaxeřqen zi jjihet n weysum zi zzariɛet n taddart n Dawud, \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Mt. 1:1; Lk. 1:32; Řex. 2:30; 13:23; 2 Tim. 2:8. \x*  
\v 4 \add maca\add* zi jjihet n jjehd d Arruḥ Iqeddsen i dd-issnekkaren Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, Siditneɣ, zi taddart n imettinen, aqa ittwassargeb d Mmis n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Ica. 9:5; 44:6; 54:5; Yḥ. 2:19; Rum. 9:5; 1 Yḥ. 5:20. \x*  
\v 5 Maɣar zzayes i neṭṭef arḍa u zzayes i nettwařaɣa d rrusul jar marra řegnus ḥima ad ṭṭaɛen \add řegnus\add* i l’iman deg Yisem nnes,  
\v 6 maɣar uřa d kenniw tᵉttwařaɣam \add zi řegnus\add* s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 7 Ɣar marra inni iǧan di Ruma, \add a\add* imɛizzen n AREBBI, inni ittwařaɣan d inni d imqeddasen: arḍa d řehna ad kidwem iřin zi AREBBI Babatneɣ u zi Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Kur. 1:2; Afa. 1:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Amezwar ttcekkareɣ AREBBI inu s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ zi jjihet nwem marra, minzi l’iman nwem aqa sřin xas di ddunect marra.  
\v 9 Maɣar AREBBI, wenni ɛebbdeɣ di Arruḥ di L’Injil n Mmis, iched xafi aqa necc ttidareɣ kenniw řebda di tẓaǧitin inu. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Rum. 9:1; 2 Kur. 1:23; 11:31; Gal. 1:20; Fil. 1:8; 1 Ts. 2:5; 2 Tim. 1:3. \x*  
\v 10 Ttẓaǧiɣ ad ayi tᵉttwarzem zi řexxu d tsawent ict n tewwart s array n AREBBI, maḥend ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Rum. 15:23,32. \x*  
\v 11 Minzi weḥḥceɣ ad kenniw ẓareɣ u ad awem wceɣ ca n tmewca n Arruḥ, ḥima ad dayes tᵉttwassmetnem. \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Rum. 15:29; 1 Ts. 3:10. \x*  
\v 12 Ad nettwassfewwej jmiɛ s l’iman nwem d wenni inu.  
\v 13 Maca xseɣ, \add a\add* aytma, ad tessnem belli aṭṭas n imuren ggiɣ ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ, \add maca\add* ař ass-a ttwamenɛeɣ, ḥima ad ɣari tiři řɣiǧet daywem ɛawed, am mammec di řegnus nneɣni, \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt 1 Ts. 2:18. \x*  
\v 14 \add maɣar\add* Necc d bu-umarwas maḥend ad barrḥeɣ \add s L’Injil\add* i Iyunaniyyen u i ibarbariyyen, i ayt n tiɣit u i ibuhařiyyen, i marra iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt 1 Kur. 9:16. \x*  
\v 15 Ammu i ttwajebdeɣ maḥend ad barrḥeɣ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan uřa i kenniw i yeǧan di Ruma.  
\v 16 Minzi war ttseḍḥiɣ ca s L’Injil, minzi netta d jjehd n AREBBI i Tudart i marra wi yumnen, \add i yinni yumnen\add* zeg Wudayen ɣar umezwar, uca \add xenni ɛawed i yinni\add* zeg Iramiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Izhd. 40:10; 1 Kur. 1:18; 15:2; 2 Tim. 1:8. \x*  
\v 17 Minzi tasegda n AREBBI aqa tban dayes \add di L’Injil\add* zi l’iman ɣar l’iman, am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Amseggad s l’iman ad iddar.’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Ḥab. 2:4; Yḥ. 3:36; Rum. 3:21; Gal. 3:11; Fil. 3:9; Ɛbr. 10:38. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Lɣaḍab n Arebbi  
\m
\v 18 Minzi aɣḍab n AREBBI ittban-dd zeg ujenna x marra řmuɛṣiyyet d tuɛeffna n iwdan inni issdurruyen tidett s řmuɛṣiyyet,  
\v 19 minzi tussna n AREBBI ittban daysen, minzi AREBBI aqa isscen asen t-i-dd. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt Řex. 14:17. \x*  
\v 20 Minzi min innuffaren n AREBBI, aqa ittwaẓar s řeɛqeř s yinni zzayes dd-ittwaxeřqen zeg wami tᵉttwagg ddunect, am jjehd nnes n řebda, am tifras nnes n AREBBI, ařami nitni war ɣarsen bu smaḥet. \x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Izhd. 19:2. \x*  
\v 21 Minzi, umi ssnen AREBBI, war t ssɛuǧen niɣ war t cekkaren am AREBBI, maca dewřen beṭṭřen deg ixariṣṣen nsen uca uř nsen ibarcen, ařami idweř břa ɛeqř. \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt Aɛwd. 28:28 \x*  
\v 22 Umi ḥessben ixef nsen d imiɣisen, dewřen d ifɣař,  
\v 23 beddřen aɛuǧi n AREBBI i war ifennin s ca deg warwas n ṣṣifet n bnadem ifennan, deg warwas n ijḍaḍ, n \add imuddaren\add* s arebɛa n iḍaren u n \add imuddaren\add* nni ittbuɛen x temmurt. \f ◼ \fr 1:23 \ft \+fk imuddaren\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘iwdan’ d ‘lḥayawanat’ d marra min iddaren nni izemmar ad yuyur.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt 2 Ij. 17:29. \x*   
\m
\v 24 \bd S uyenni\bd* isellem i-ten AREBBI ɣar nnecwat ixemjen n wuřawen nsen ḥima ad ssfeḍḥen arrimat nsen jar asen.  
\v 25 Aqa nitni beddřen tidett n AREBBI s uxarriq, ɛebden u sexxaren i min dd-ittwaxeřqen sennej i Wenni dd-ixeřqen kuřci, Wenni umi ɣar iǧa \add marra\add* asemɣar d \add marra\add* lbarakat i řebda qaɛ. Amin.   
\b  
\m
\v 26 \bd S uyenni\bd* isellem i-ten AREBBI ɣar ccehwat infeḍḥen, minzi uřa d timɣarin nsen beddřent abrid n ṭṭbiɛet, ttnumant i min war iǧin d ṭṭbiɛet. \x ◘ \xo 1:26 \xt Lawi 18:22, 23. \x*  
\v 27 Amenni iryazen ɛawed jjin tamunt ɛlaḥsab ṭṭbiɛet ak-d temɣarin, deɛqen s nnecwat ak-d wayawya: iryazen i itteggen řefḍiḥet ak-d yeryazen uca qebbřen deg ixef nsen řmunet i isdaheǧen i uweddar nsen.  
\v 28 Minzi war xsen ad kksen awař maḥend ad ssnen AREBBI, isellem i-ten AREBBI ɣar řeɛqeř war isekkwin ḥima ad ggen min war iɛeddřen.  
\v 29 Nitni ɛemmaren s ɛřam kuř řmuɛṣiyyet, s farq-ccɣeř d tarzugi d tuɛeffna d ṭṭmeɛ, s řeḥsed d wenɣay d umenɣi d teḥraymect d inwayen iɛeffnen.  
\v 30 \add Nitni\add* ssawařen s řɣar, ttceqqafen, carrhen AREBBI, \add nitni\add* d imeɣṣaben d imɛeffaren d ayt n bu-uqemmum d imesuffɣen n tuɛeffna, war ɣarsen bu řɛqeř, \add nitni\add* war ṭṭiɛen i lwalidin nsen,  
\v 31 war daysen \add uř\add* imten, war daysen tayri d weṣřaḥ uřa d arreḥmet.  
\v 32 Waxxa nitni ssnen řḥukm n AREBBI - aqa inni itteggen aya sdaheǧen řmewt - nitni war tteggen \add marra\add* man aya waha, maca areṭṭan ɛawed x yinni itteggen timesřayin-a. \x ◘ \xo 1:32 \xt Ḥuc. 7:3. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Řḥukm iseggden n Arebbi  
\m
\v 1 \bd S uyenni\bd* aqa cek břa smaḥet, a bnadem, cek d wenni iḥekkmen x wenni d ac yudsen, minzi di min tḥekkmed x umeddukkeř nnec, aqa uřa d cek d bu-umarwas di man aya, maɣar cek, wenni ittḥasaben \add inneɣni\add*, řesqent ɣarek uřa d simant n tmesřayin. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt 2 Ṣm. 12:5; Mt. 7:1; 1 Kur. 4:5. \x*  
\v 2 Neccin nessen belli řḥukm n AREBBI d tidett x yinni ɣar teǧa tesɣart di tmesřayin am tina.  
\v 3 Maca mayemmi d ac ittɣiř, \add a\add* bnadem, wenni iḥekkmen x yinni itteggen timesřayin-a am uřa d cek tᵉttegged tent simant nnec, aqa tzemmared ad tarewřed zi řḥukm n AREBBI?  
\v 4 Niɣ tesseḥqarad agřa n tcuni nnes d ttasiɛ n uraji nnes d ttasiɛ i d ac iwcin, uca war tessined ca belli tcuni n AREBBI aqa ineddeh i cek ɣar ttubet? \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 2 Bṭ. 3:15. \x*  
\v 5 Maca di ssibbet n řeqsaḥet d nnuqṣan n ttubet n wuř nnec, tyarwed i yixef nnec ijj n řeqdar n weɣḍab i wass n weɣḍab u i usargeb n řḥukm iseggden n AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Rum. 9:22. \x*  
\v 6 wenni i ɣa ixeǧṣen kuř ijjen ɛlaḥsab řexdayem nnes: \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Izhd. 62:13; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 14:12; 1 Kur. 3:8; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Asa. 2:23; 22:12. \x*   
\m
\v 7 ... i yinni yarezzun aɛuǧi d ccan d min war ifennin am ttṣebbaren nitni di řexdayem iṣebḥen, \add aqa ad asen ixeǧeṣ s\add* Tudart ittduman,   
\m
\v 8 ... maca i yinni ittɣewwɣen, inni war ittnumen ttᵉṭṭaɛen i tidett, maca ttnumen ttᵉṭṭaɛen i min war iseggden, aqa ad asen ixeǧeṣ s weɣḍab d tefqeḥt, \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt 2 Ts. 1:8. \x*   
\m
\v 9 ... u s řmeḥnet d řeḥsaret ad ixeǧeṣ kuř řeɛmar n bnadem i itteggen řɣar, Udayen d amezwar, \add xenni\add* Iramiyyen,   
\m
\v 10 ... maca aɛuǧi d ccan d řehna \add ad iřin\add* i marra wi itteggen tcuni, i Wudayen d amezwar uca \add xenni\add* i Iramiyyen,  
\v 11 minzi AREBBI war ittegg ca s wudmawen. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Aɛwd. 10:17; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 34:19; Řex. 10:34; Gal. 2:6; Afa. 6:9; Kul. 3:25; 1 Bṭ. 1:17. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Minzi marra inni ɣa ixḍan břa Ccariɛa, břa Ccariɛa ad ttwahellken uca marra inni ɣa ixḍan sadu Ccariɛa, aqa s Ccariɛa ad ttwaḥasben  
\v 13 maɣar war iǧi inni ittesřan i Ccariɛa nitni d imseggaden ɣar AREBBI, maca inni itteggen Ccariɛa aqa nitni ad ttwaseggden. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Mt. 7:21; Yaɛ. 1:22; 1 Yḥ. 3:7. \x*  
\v 14 Minzi mařa řegnus nni war ɣar iǧi bu Ccariɛa, tteggen s ṭṭbiɛet min dayes di Ccariɛa, aqa yina d Ccariɛa i yixef nsen, waxxa nitni war ɣarsen bu Ccariɛa,  
\v 15 uca sscanen belli řxedmet n Ccariɛa tura deg wuřawen nsen, am teched ɛawed tnefsect nsen, am ixarriṣen nsen deǧen uřa ttdafaɛen x yixef nsen jar asen \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Irm. 31:33\x*  
\v 16 deg wass min di i ɣa iḥaseb AREBBI x min innufaren deg iwdan s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ɛlaḥsab L’Injil inu. \x ◘ \xo 2:16 \xt Mt. 25:31. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Uday d Ccariɛa  
\m
\v 17 Maca mařa cek, umi řaɣan Uday, tsennaded x Ccariɛa u tessemɣared di AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Rum. 9:4. \x*  
\v 18 aqa tessned min ixs Netta, tfarrzed min iṣebḥen, minzi tᵉttwassřemded zi Ccariɛa,  
\v 19 u tḥasbed ixef nnec d amgewwed n idarɣařen d tfawt i yinni iǧan di taǧest,  
\v 20 d amseggem yarebban ibuhařiyyen d amseřmad n iḥenjiren, u aqa ɣarek ṣṣifet n tussna d tidett di Ccariɛa,  
\v 21 \add iwa\add* cek wenni isseřmaden inneɣni, ma war tesseřmided ca ixef nnec? Cek wenni ittbarrḥen ‘War tticar!’, ma tᵉttacared?  
\v 22 Cek wenni iqqaren ‘War zenni!’, ma tzennid? Cek d wenni icarrhen l’aṣnam, ma tacared zzawect \add nsen\add* iqeddsen? \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Řex. 19:37\x*  
\v 23 Cek wenni issemɣaran di Ccariɛa, ma tfeḍḥed AREBBI umi texḍid di Ccariɛa?  
\v 24 Minzi x ssibbet nwem ttceqqafen deg Yisem n AREBBI jar řegnus am mammec tura. \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt Ica. 52:5; Ḥiz. 36:2. \x*   
\m
\v 25 Aqa axtan ineffeɛ mařa tḍeffared Ccariɛa nican, maca mařa tᵉttɛeddid x Ccariɛa, aqa axtan nnec ittwaḥseb břa axtan.  
\v 26 Mařa wenni břa axtan ittᵉṭṭef di řumar iseggden n Ccariɛa, ma \add xenni\add* war iḥesseb břa axtan nnes d axtan?  
\v 27 Wenni iḍeffaren Ccariɛa s ṭṭbiɛet am iǧa břa axtan, ad cek iḥaseb, cek wenni ittɛeddan x Ccariɛa s Tira d wextan!  
\v 28 Minzi Uday war iǧi d Uday s wudem, u axtan \add s tidett\add* war iǧi min ittbanen deg weysum, \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Yḥ. 8:39; Rum. 9:7. \x*  
\v 29 maca netta d Uday wenni ittiřin d Uday di tnuffra, u axtan aqa netta d wenni deg wuř, s Arruḥ, war iǧi \add d wenni ittwaggen\add* ɛlaḥsab Tirra \add n Ccariɛa\add*, ařami asemɣar nnes war dd-ittis ca zeg iwdan maca zi AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 2:29 \xt Aɛwd. 10:16; Irm. 4:4; Fil. 3:2, 3; Kul. 2:11. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Arebbi d tidett u kuř bnadem dayes řɣecc  
\m
\v 1 I xenni, man řefḍeř ɣar Wudayen, niɣ man tizi n wextan?  
\v 2 Aṭṭas x kuř iɣezdisen! Xenni ɣar umezwar mmewcen asen ‬wawařen n‮ ‬AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Izhd. 147:19; Rum. 9:4. \x*  
\v 3 Maɣar mařa tuɣa ca zzaysen war uminen ca, ma xenni beḍřen nitni řaman n AREBBI zi ssibbet n břa l’iman nsen? \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt Řxř. 23:19; Rum. 9:6; 2 Tim. 2:13. \x*  
\v 4 Ɛemmarṣ! Maɣar AREBBI d tidett uca kuř bnadem d bu-ixarriqen, am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Cek ad tbaned d Amsegged s wawařen nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt ad tiřid tkemmřed di řeṣfayet\qt*  
\m \qt xmi Cek i ɣa ḥasben.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Izhd. 51:6; 116:11; Yḥ. 3:33. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Maca mařa min war isseggden dayneɣ aqa issbeyyen tasegda n AREBBI, min ɣa nini ɛad xenni? Ma AREBBI war ɣares bu řḥeqq umi xaneɣ igga aɣḍab nnes? Necc ssawařeɣ am yijj n bnadem \add d amednub\add*.  
\v 6 War xas nessiwiř! Mammec i ɣa iḥaseb AREBBI ddunect řexdenni?  
\v 7 Mammec mařa tfeyyeḍ tidett n AREBBI ɣar uɛuǧi nnes s uxarriq inu, mayemmi ɛad i ɣa ttwaḥasbeɣ am umednub?  
\v 8 War iɛeddeř aqa tamesřact teǧa am mammec qqaren inni dayneɣ iceqqfen belli neccin neqqar: “Ejj aneɣ ad negg tuɛeffna, ḥima ad zzayes dd-yekk min icnan!”?, inni aqa řḥukm xasen ad ittwaxemmeř ař ccreɛ iseggden.   
\b  
\m
\v 9 I xenni mammec? Ma neccin ḥsen? Qbeř aqa nufa aqa Udayen d Iramiyyen marra sadu ddenb, \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Gal. 3:22. \x*  
\v 10 am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Uřa d ijj war iǧi d amsegged,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Izhd. 14:3; 53:4. \x*   
\m
\v 11 \qt uřa d ijj war ifehhem,\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d ijj war yarezzu x AREBBI.\qt*   
\m
\v 12 \qt Marra ffɣen zeg webrid, mmenḍaren,\qt*  
\m \qt uřa d ijj war ittegg tcuni, uřa d ijj.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Izhd. 14:1-3; 53:2-4; Amb. 7:20\x*   
\m
\v 13 \qt Tmijjawin nsen d imeḍřan yarezmen,\qt*  
\m \qt s iřsawen nsen cemmten,\qt*  
\m \qt ssem n ifiɣran sadu iyencicen nsen,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Izhd. 5:10; 140:4. \x*   
\m
\v 14 \qt aqemmum nsen iccur s nneɛřet d tarzugi,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:14 \xt Izhd. 10:7. \x*   
\m
\v 15 \qt s iḍaren nsen ttqeǧiqen\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar usizzeř n idammen,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Awřn. 1:16; Ica. 59:7. \x*   
\m
\v 16 \qt areyyeb d tamara deg ibriden nsen,\qt*   
\m
\v 17 \qt abrid n řehna war t ssinen ca,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 3:17 \xt Ica. 59:7, 8\x*   
\m
\v 18 \qt tiggʷudi n AREBBI\qt*  
\m \qt war teǧi qibač i tiṭṭawin nsen.”\qt*\x ◘ \xo 3:18 \xt Izhd. 36:2. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Neccin nessen belli marra min teqqar Ccariɛa, aqa teqqar i-t i yinni iǧan sadu Ccariɛa, ḥima ad ittwaqqen kuř aqemmum uca ad tedweř marra ddunect dayes řɛib zzat i AREBBI,  
\v 20 maɣar zi řexdayem n Ccariɛa war ittwasegged uřa d ijj n bnadem qibač nnes, minzi s Ccariɛa aqa ttwassnen ddnub. \x ◘ \xo 3:20 \xt Rum. 7:7; Gal. 2:16; Ɛbr. 7:18. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tasegda s l’iman weḥḥdes  
\m
\v 21 Maca řexxu aqa teḍhar-dd tsegda n AREBBI břa Ccariɛa, tcehhed xas Ccariɛa d Inabiyyen, \x ◘ \xo 3:21 \xt Rum. 1:17; Fil. 3:9. \x*  
\v 22 aqa tasegda n AREBBI zi l’iman n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ɣar marra u x marra inni zzayes yumnen, minzi war din bu řfarz.  
\v 23 Minzi marra xḍan uca ineqṣ i-ten uɛuǧi n AREBBI,  
\v 24 uca ttwaseggden baṭeř s arḍa nnes s ufekki i iǧan di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 3:24 \xt Ica. 53:5. \x*  
\v 25 AREBBI igga i-t d aṣřaḥ qbeř s l’iman deg Idammen nnes, di ssibbet n ddnub nneɣ nni tuɣa negga zic di řmijař n řweqt i d aneɣ iwca AREBBI s ttasiɛ n řxaḍar nnes, ḥima ad isscen tasegda nnes di řweqt-a, \x ◘ \xo 3:25 \xt Uf. 25:17; 2 Kur. 5:19; Kul. 1:20; Ɛbr. 4:16; 1 Yḥ. 4:10. \x*  
\v 26 maḥend di tsegda ad yarr d amseggad wi iǧan di l’iman n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\m
\v 27 Mani iǧa xenni usemɣar? War xas nessiwiř. S man Ccariɛa? S man řexdayem? Ɛemmarṣ, maca s Ccariɛa n l’iman.  
\v 28 S uya neḥseb belli bnadem ad ittwasegged s l’iman, war iǧi s řexdayem n Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 3:28 \xt Řex. 13:38; Rum. 8:3; Gal. 2:16; Ɛbr. 7:25. \x*  
\v 29 Niɣ AREBBI n Wudayen waha, war iǧi n řegnus ɛawed? Wah, uřa n řegnus!  
\v 30 Minzi AREBBI d Ijjen wenni i ɣa iseggden inni ittwaxetnen s l’iman, u ɛawed inni war ittwaxtinen s l’iman.  
\v 31 Ma nbeṭṭeř Ccariɛa s l’iman? Wayyaw, s řemqřub, neccin ad neḍmen Ccariɛa.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 4
\s1 L’iman n Ibrahim  
\m
\v 1 Min i ɣa nini xenni x Ibrahim, azeǧif n řejdud nneɣ, aqa yufa di \add arrimet nnes n\add* weysum? \x ◘ \xo 4:1 \xt Ica. 51:2. \x*  
\v 2 Minzi mařa Ibrahim tuɣa ittwasegged s řexdayem, aqa ɣares ccan, maca war iǧi ca ɣar AREBBI.  
\v 3 Minzi min qqarent Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*? “Yumen Ibrahim di AREBBI uca ittwaḥseb as-dd man aya d tasegda.” \x ◘ \xo 4:3 \xt Amz. 15:6; Gal. 3:6; Yaɛ. 2:23. \x*  
\v 4 Wenni ixeddmen war d as tᵉttwaḥesseb ca řmunet x řeḥsab n arḍa, maca x řeḥsab n umarwas, \add minzi ttursen as-dd\add*.  
\v 5 Maca wenni war ixeddmen, maca yumen deg Wenni ittseggaden imednab, aqa l’iman nnes ad as dd-ittwaḥseb d tasegda.  
\v 6 Am mammec inna Dawud ɛawed x sseɛd n bnadem wenni umi dd as iḥseb AREBBI tasegda břa řexdayem, umi inna:   
\b  
\m
\v 7 \qt “Sseɛd n yinni umi ittwaɣfar ixeṭṭan nsen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni umi issduriy \+tl Netta\+tl* ddnub nsen.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Izhd. 32:1. \x*   
\m
\v 8 \qt Sseɛd n bnadem\qt*  
\m \qt umi war dd as iḥesseb ca\qt*  
\m \qt AREBBI ddnub nnes.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 4:8 \xt Izhd. 32:1, 2\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Ma sseɛd-a x yinni ittwaxetnen waha niɣ ɛawed x yinni war ittwaxetnen? S minzi neqqar: “L’iman n Ibrahim ittwaḥseb as-dd d tasegda!” \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Amz. 15:6\x*  
\v 10 Mammec d as t-i-dd ittwaḥseb? Ma řami tuɣa s wextan niɣ mařa tuɣa břa axtan? War tuɣi s wextan, maca tuɣa břa axtan.  
\v 11 Minzi iksi axtan d řeɛřamet d ucemmiɛ n tsegda n l’iman nni ɣares umi t tuɣa břa axtan, ḥima ad yiři d jedditsen n marra inni yumnen waxxa nitni břa axtan, ḥima ad asen dd-ittwaḥseb \add l’iman\add* d tasegda ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Amz. 17:11. \x*  
\v 12 Netta d jedditsen i yinni s wextan, \add maca\add* war iǧi i yinni \add idewřen yumnen\add* zeg wextan waha, \add maca\add* ɛawed i yinni igguren deg iṣuraf n l’iman n jedditneɣ Ibrahim umi tuɣa břa axtan.   
\m
\v 13 Minzi lwaɛd i Ibrahim u i zzariɛet nnes belli ad yiři d awrit n ddunect, war dd-ittis ca s Ccariɛa, maca s tsegda n l’iman nnes.  
\v 14 Minzi mařa inni zi Ccariɛa d iwriten, aqa l’iman ixessaren uřa d lwaɛd ibeḍřen. \x ◘ \xo 4:14 \xt Gal. 3:18. \x*  
\v 15 Maɣar Ccariɛa tᵉttaru aɣḍab. Mani war teǧi Ccariɛa, war din iǧi uřa d aɛeddi n Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt Yḥ. 15:22; Rum. 5:20; 7:8; Gal. 3:19. \x*   
\m
\v 16 S uyenni nettwasegged s l’iman, ixs ad yini s arḍa, maḥend ad yiři lwaɛd nican i qaɛ zzariɛet nnes, war iǧi i yinni iǧan zi Ccariɛa waha, maca ɛawed i yinni iǧan zi l’iman n Ibrahim, wenni d jedditneɣ n marra idneɣ, \x ◘ \xo 4:16 \xt Ica. 51:2. \x*  
\v 17 am mammec tura: “Aqa ggiɣ cek d jedditsen i waṭṭas n řegnus!”, zzat i AREBBI Wenni zi tuɣa tumned, wenni itticen Tudart i imettinen d wenni ittřaɣan timesřayin i war iǧin axmi ǧan. \x ◘ \xo 4:17 \xt Amz. 17:5. \x*  
\v 18 Waxxa iqḍeɛ as řayas, aqa yumen s usitem ad idweř d jedditsen i waṭṭas n řegnus am mammec tura: “Ammu i ɣa tiři zzariɛet nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 4:18 \xt Amz. 15:5; Ɛbr. 11:12. \x*  
\v 19 L’iman nnes war tuɣi iḍɛef, umi iḥseb arrimet nnes temmut am tuɣa ɣares mya n iseggʷusa, u umi immut uɛeddis n Sara.  
\v 20 Netta war icekk ca di lwaɛd n AREBBI axmi s nneqṣ n l’iman, maca imḥeḍ di l’iman nnes, iwca aɛuǧi i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 4:20 \xt Yḥ. 8:56; Ɛbr. 11:11, 18. \x*  
\v 21 Tuɣa issen nican belli min zzayes tuɣa iwaɛd AREBBI, izemmar ad t igg ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 4:21 \xt Izhd. 115:3. \x*  
\v 22 S uyenni ittwaḥseb as-dd \add l’iman\add* d tasegda. \x ◘ \xo 4:22 \xt Amz. 15:6. \x*   
\m
\v 23 Maca war turi di ssibbet nnes waha, aqa ittwaḥseb as-dd l’iman nnes d tasegda, \x ◘ \xo 4:23 \xt Rum. 15:4. \x*  
\v 24 maca ɛawed di ssibbet nneɣ, ḥima Netta ad aneɣ t-i-dd-iḥseb \add d tasegda\add*, i neccin inni ittamnen deg Wenni i dd-issnekkaren Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ zi taddart n imettinen,  
\v 25 \add Yeccu Lmasiḥ\add* wenni ittwasellmen di ssibbet n ddnub nneɣ uca ikkar-dd ḥima ad aneɣ isegged.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 5
\s1 Tayri n Arebbi s Lmasiḥ deg wuřawen nneɣ  
\m
\v 1 Xenni neccin, am nettwasegged s l’iman, aqa ad ɣarneɣ yiři řehna ak-d AREBBI s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 5:1 \xt Ica. 32:17; Yḥ. 16:33; Afa. 2:13. \x*  
\v 2 Maɣar zzayes idweř aneɣ-dd adaf s l’iman ɣar arḍa-ya min di nbedd, u nessemɣar deg usitem n uɛuǧi n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 5:2 \xt Yḥ. 10:9; 14:6; 1 Kur. 15:1; Afa. 2:18; 3:12; Ɛbr. 3:6; 10:19. \x*  
\v 3 \add Maca\add* war iǧi di man aya waha, maca nessemɣar ɛawed di řemḥayem, nessen belli řmeḥnet tᵉttaru-dd dayneɣ ṣṣbar, \x ◘ \xo 5:3 \xt Yaɛ. 1:3. \x*  
\v 4 d ṣṣbar \add ad yawi\add* taqeǧebt, uca taqeǧebt \add ad tawi\add* asitem,  
\v 5 uca asitem war ittseḥcim ca, minzi tayri n AREBBI aqa tᵉttwafarreɣ deg wuřawen nneɣ s Arruḥ Iqeddsen i d aneɣ immewcen.   
\m
\v 6 Di ssibbet n tuḍɛeft nneɣ, aqa immut Lmasiḥ di řweqt-a di ṭṭweɛ n iɛeffanen. \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Afa. 2:1; Kul. 2:13; Ɛbr. 9:15; 1 Bṭ. 3:18. \x*  
\v 7 S řweḥřan ad immet ḥed di ṭṭweɛ n ijj n uɛeffan, maca di ṭṭweɛ n iṣebḥanen ad taɣ izemmar ad izɛem ḥed ad immet.  
\v 8 Di man aya imřa aneɣ AREBBI tayri nnes, aqa Lmasiḥ immut di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ umi tuɣa aneɣ ɛad d imednab. \x ◘ \xo 5:8 \xt Ɛbr. 9:15; 1 Bṭ. 3:18. \x*  
\v 9 Mecḥař ktar aqa nettwasegged řexxu s Idammen nnes uca nettwafekk zzayes zeg weɣḍab!  
\v 10 Minzi řami d aneɣ tuɣa d řɛedyan, ijja AREBBI ad isseṣřeḥ Ixef nnes akidneɣ s řmewt n Mmis, mecḥař qaɛ řexxu ad neddar s Tudart nnes, awarni řami zzayes nufa aṣřaḥ.  
\v 11 U war iǧi man aya waha, maca ad nessemɣar di AREBBI ɛawed s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, wenni zi neksi řexxu aṣřaḥ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Adam d Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 12 Maɣar am mammec s yijj n bnadem yudef-dd ddenb ɣar ddunect uca s ddenb tudef-dd řmewt, ammu dd-tudef řmewt ɣar iwdan marra, minzi xḍan marra. \x ◘ \xo 5:12 \xt Amz. 2:17; 3:6; 1 Kur. 15:21. \x*  
\v 13 Minzi qbeř ma tuɣa teǧa Ccariɛa, tuɣa ddenb di ddunect, maca ddenb war ittwaḥsib ca minzi war din teǧi Ccariɛa.  
\v 14 Maca řmewt tuɣa teḥkem zi Adam ař Musa uřa x yinni war ixḍin di ṣṣifet n uxeṭṭu i zi ixḍa Adam ak-d ccariɛa. \add Adam\add* wenni d ṣṣifet n Wenni dd ɣa yasen.   
\m
\v 15 Maca am mammec teǧi \add tmesřact\add* s uweṭṭu, ammu war teǧi s tewhibt n arḍa. Minzi mařa mmuten aṭṭas x ssibbet n ijj n uxeṭṭu, mecḥař qaɛ i ɣa ifeyyeḍ arḍa n AREBBI d tewhibt nnes i waṭṭas s uyenni n Bnadem \add nni\add*, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 16 Tawhibt s arḍa war tᵉttiři am uxeṭṭu n yijjen. S minzi řḥukm yiwi-dd lḥisab zeg ijj n uxeṭṭu, maca tawhibt n arḍa tiwi-dd zeg waṭṭas n ddnub ɣar tsegda.  
\v 17 Minzi mařa s uxeṭṭu n ijjen aqa teḥkem řmewt, mecḥař qaɛ i ɣa ḥekmen di Tudart inni iksin afeyyeḍ n arḍa d tewhibt n tsegda s uyenni \add n bnadem nni\add*, aqa-t d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\m
\v 18 Am mammec xenni s uxeṭṭu n ijjen, aqa idweř řḥukm i marra iwdan, ammu i ɣa tiři řeṣfayet ikemmřen i Tudart i marra iwdan s tsegda n Yijjen.  
\v 19 Minzi am s řmuɛṣiyyet n ijj n bnadem dewřen aṭṭas d imednab, ammu ɛawed s ṭṭaɛet n Ijjen ad dewřen aṭṭas d imseggaden.  
\v 20 Maca umi dd-tusa Ccariɛa, immarni ddenb, u mani immarni ddenb, immarni arḍa aṭṭas s waṭṭas, \x ◘ \xo 5:20 \xt Luik. 7:47; Yḥ. 15:22; Rum. 4:15; 7:8; Gal. 3:19\x*  
\v 21 ḥima, am mammec iḥkem ddenb ař řmewt, ad iḥkem arḍa ɛawed s tsegda ař Tudart ittduman s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 6
\s1 Aseɣḍeṣ di Lmasiḥ  
\m
\v 1 Min ɣa nini xenni? Ma ad neqqim di ddenb ḥima ad immarni arḍa?  
\v 2 Ɛemmarṣ! Neccin inni immuten i ddenb, mammec ɛad dayes i ɣa neddar?  
\v 3 Ma war tessinem ca belli inni zzayneɣ ittwassɣeḍṣen di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ttwassɣeḍṣen di řmewt nnes? \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Gal. 3:27. \x*  
\v 4 Aqa nettwanḍeř akides s useɣḍeṣ di řmewt, ḥima, am mammec dd-ittwassnekkar Lmasiḥ zi taddart n imettinen ɣar uɛuǧi n Babas, ammu i ɣa nuyur uřa d neccin di Tudart n jdid. \x ◘ \xo 6:4 \xt Rum. 8:11; Afa. 4:23; Fil. 3:10, 11; Kul. 2:12; 3:10; Ɛbr. 12:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:2. \x*  
\v 5 Minzi mařa nettwaẓẓu \add di temmurt\add* d ijjen akides s \add tefras n\add* řmewt nnes, xenni ammu i ɣa niři ɛawed \add d ijjen akides\add* s tefras n tnukra nnes. \x ◘ \xo 6:5 \xt Rum. 8:11; Kul. 3:1. \x*  
\v 6 Aqa nessen belli bnadem nneɣ aqdim ittwaṣelleb akides, ḥima ad tebḍeř arrimet n ddenb, war ndikkwiř ɛawed d imsexxaren i ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Gal. 2:20; 5:24; Fil. 3:10; 1 Bṭ. 4:1, 2. \x*  
\v 7 Minzi wenni immuten, aqa ittwafekk zi ddnub. \x ◘ \xo 6:7 \xt 1 Bṭ. 4:1. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Mařa xenni nemmut ak-d Lmasiḥ, aqa numen belli neddar \add ɛawed\add* akides, ak-d Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 6:8 \xt 2 Tim. 2:11. \x*  
\v 9 Minzi nessen belli Lmasiḥ ittwassnekkar-dd zi taddart n imettinen, war ittmetti ɛawed. Aqa řmewt war xas tḥekkem ca. \x ◘ \xo 6:9 \xt Asa. 1:18. \x*  
\v 10 Minzi zeg uɣezdis n řmewt i immut, aqa immut i ddnub ijj n umur, maca zeg uɣezdis n Tudart nnes, Netta iddar i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt 1 Bṭ. 2:24. \x*  
\v 11 Ammu kenniw ɛawed: ḥesbem ixef nwem d imettinen i ddenb, \add maca\add* d imuddaren i AREBBI di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\m
\v 12 Xenni war ttejjim ddenb ad iḥkem di arrimet nwem ifennan, ařami ad as tᵉṭṭaɛem di nnecwat nnes,  
\v 13 uca war ttewcim iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* nwem am dduzan i řmuɛṣiyyet, maca wcem ixef nwem i AREBBI, am iwdan inni idewřen ɣar Tudart zeg imettinen, uca \add wcem\add* iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* nwem am dduzan i tsegda n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 6:13 \xt Lk. 1:74; Rum. 12:1; Gal. 2:20; Ɛbr. 9:14; 1 Bṭ. 4:2. \x*  
\v 14 Ddenb war xawem iḥekkem ca, minzi war teǧim sadu Ccariɛa maca sadu arḍa.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Imsexxaren n tsegda  
\m
\v 15 Mammec xenni? Ma ad nexḍa minzi war neǧi ca sadu Ccariɛa, maca sadu arḍa? Ɛemmarṣ!  
\v 16 Ma war tessinem ca aqa kenniw d imsexxaren n wenni umi tewcim ixef nwem maḥend ad as tsexxarem s ṭṭaɛet, n wenni umi tᵉttᵉṭṭaɛem, ma i ddenb i tᵉttᵉṭṭaɛem niɣ i tsegda? \x ◘ \xo 6:16 \xt Yḥ. 8:34; 2 Bṭ. 2:19. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Tqad as i AREBBI, aqa kenniw inni tuɣa d imsexxaren i ddenb, aqa tdewřem tᵉttᵉṭṭaɛem s wuř i ddab \add iṣfan\add* n useřmed i d awem ittwasellmen.  
\v 18 Řami tᵉttwafekkem zi ddenb, tdewřem d imsexxaren n tsegda. \x ◘ \xo 6:18 \xt Yḥ. 8:32; Gal. 5:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:16. \x*  
\v 19 Ssawařeɣ x řeḥsab řeɛqeř n bnadem x ssibbet n tuḍɛeft n weysum nwem, minzi am mammec tewcim iɣezdisen nwem d imsexxaren i řexmej d min war iseggden, amenni řexxu wcem iɣezdisen nwem d imsexxaren i tsegda d tqeddast.  
\v 20 Minzi řami tuɣa kenniw d imsexxaren n ddenb, tuɣa kenniw d iḥurriyyen zi jjihet n tsegda. \x ◘ \xo 6:20 \xt Yḥ. 8:34. \x*  
\v 21 Man řɣiǧet i tuɣa ɣarwem řexdenni? Timesřayin i zi tᵉttseḍḥam řexxu? S minzi aneggar nsent d řmewt.  
\v 22 \add Maca\add* řexxu, umi tᵉttwafekkem zi ddenb uca tdewřem d imsexxaren n AREBBI, aqa řɣiǧet nwem tᵉttwaqeddes uca uneggar nnes d Tudart ittduman.  
\v 23 Minzi řexřaṣ n ddenb d řmewt, maca tawhibt n AREBBI d Tudart ittduman s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Amz. 2:17; Rum. 5:12; 1 Kur. 15:21; Yaɛ. 1:15. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 7
\s1 Amettiř n řemřac  
\m
\v 1 Ma war tessinem ca, \add a\add* aytma, ssawařeɣ ak-d yinni issnen Ccariɛa, aqa Ccariɛa tṣeǧeḍ x bnadem min ɣa yekk iddar?  
\v 2 Tamɣart teqqen ɣar weryaz nnes s Ccariɛa min ɣa yekk iddar, maca mařa immut weryaz nnes, aqa tᵉttwafekk zi Ccariɛa zi jjihet n weryaz nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:2 \xt 1 Kur. 7:2, 10,39. \x*  
\v 3 Maca mařa ad teqqen ɣar weryaz nneɣni min ɣa yekk weryaz iddar, tᵉttwaḥseb zzayes aqa nettat tezna. Maca mařa immut weryaz nnes, ad taf ad tᵉttwafekk zi Ccariɛa, aqa war tezni mařa temřec ak-d weryaz nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Mt. 5:32. \x*  
\v 4 Xenni, \add a\add* aytma, kenniw ɛawed aqa temmutem i Ccariɛa s Arrimet n Lmasiḥ, ḥima ad tdewřem i Wenneɣni i wenni dd-ikkaren zi taddart n imettinen, ḥima ad tewcem řɣiǧet i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 7:4 \xt Gal. 2:19; 1 Bṭ. 4:1. \x*  
\v 5 Minzi umi d aneɣ tuɣa deg weysum, tuɣa ccehwat n ddnub xeddment deg iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* nneɣ am ttwaɛarnent zi Ccariɛa ařami ɣa awyent řɣiǧet i řmewt.  
\v 6 Maca řexxu aqa nettwafekk zi Ccariɛa, aqa nemmut x min di tuɣa nettwaḥbes, ḥima ad neɛbed \add AREBBI\add* s tejdidet n Arruḥ, war iǧi di ṣṣifet taqdimt n Tira \add Iqeddsen\add*. \f ◼ \fr 7:6 \ft \+bd 'war iǧi di ṣṣifet taqdimt n Tira \+bdit Iqeddsen\+bdit*'\+bd* - Tira Iqeddsen ssawařent x Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. Netta d Atarras Amezwaru n Wedlis Iqeddsen zeg wedlis Umezwaru ař adlis n Usargeb ɣar uneggar nnes. Wenni iqqaren Adlis Iqeddsen (ixs ad yina Tira Iqeddsen) neḥřa ma issen Utarras Amezwaru n Wedlis, iǧa di teqdimt n Tira Iqeddsen, ixs ad yini, netta iqqar břa ma ittwaři Atarras nni Amezwaru, netta am ijj n bnadem d adarɣař. Adlis i iqqar, war iddar i netta, maca i netta d adlis nni am ijj n umetta. S uyenni wenni iqqaren ammu, aqa netta di teqdimt n Tira Iqeddsen, war iǧi di tmaynut n Arruḥ. Maɣar mɣir mařa ijj n bnadem issen Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ s wuř u s liman, ad iqbeř Arruḥ Iqeddsen uřa d tamaynut n Arruḥ di daxeř nnes uca ad iɣar Adlis Iqeddsen s yijj n ccekl d jdid, minzi Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ Netta d Atarras Amezwaru n Wedlis Iqeddsen.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:6 \xt Rum. 2:29; 2 Kur. 3:6. \x*   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amenɣi ak-d ddnub  
\m
\v 7 Min ɣa nini xenni? Ma Ccariɛa d ddenb? Ɛemmarṣ! Maca war ssineɣ ddenb mɣir s Ccariɛa waha, maɣar war ssineɣ nnecwet mařa war tenni Ccariɛa: “War ttasem!” \x ◘ \xo 7:7 \xt Uf. 20:17; Aɛwd. 5:21; Rum. 3:20; Ɛbr. 7:18. \x*  
\v 8 Maca ddenb yufa lfurṣa s tewṣeyyet uca tegma dayi kuř nnecwet, minzi břa Ccariɛa ddenb immut. \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt Yḥ. 15:22; Rum. 4:15; 5:20; Gal. 3:19. \x*  
\v 9 Zic tuɣa ddareɣ břa Ccariɛa, maca umi dd-tusa tewṣeyyet, ibda ddenb ad iddar, uca mmuteɣ.  
\v 10 Ufiɣ belli tawṣeyyet i iǧan i tudart tneddeh ɣar řmewt.  
\v 11 Minzi ddenb am yufa lfurṣa s tewṣeyyet, icmet ayi uca inɣa ayi zzayes.  
\v 12 Xenni Ccariɛa iqeddsen i teǧa u tawṣeyyet iqeddsen i teǧa, tsegged u teṣbeḥ. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt 1 Tim. 1:8. \x*   
\m
\v 13 Ma idweř ayi min iǧan d aṣebḥan d řmewt inu? Ɛemmarṣ! Maca ddenb, ḥima ad iban d ddenb, issegma dayi řmewt s min iǧan d aṣebḥan, ḥima ad idweř ddenb d ddenb ktar s tewṣiyyet.  
\v 14 Aqa nessen belli Ccariɛa n Arruḥ i teǧa, maca necc d aysum, mmenzeɣ i ddenb, \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Ica. 52:3. \x*  
\v 15 minzi war ssineɣ min ɣa ggeɣ, uca min xseɣ, war t tteggeɣ, maca min carrheɣ d manawenni i tteggeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt Gal. 5:17. \x*  
\v 16 Mařa tteggeɣ min war ttexseɣ, ad wafqeɣ ak-d Ccariɛa, belli aqa nettat teṣbeḥ.  
\v 17 Maca řexxu necc war tteggeɣ man aya \add ɛad\add*, maca ddenb i d ayi izeddɣen \add ittegg i-t\add*.  
\v 18 Minzi ssneɣ war dayi izeddeɣ min icnan, ixs ad yini deg weysum inu. Minzi ihwen xafi maḥend ad xseɣ tcuni, maca war zemmareɣ ad tt ggeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 7:18 \xt Amz. 6:5; 8:21. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi war tteggeɣ tcuni i xseɣ, maca řɣar i war ttexseɣ ca, d manawenni i tteggeɣ.  
\v 20 Mařa tteggeɣ min war ttexseɣ, war iǧi ɛad d necc i itteggen man aya, maca ddenb wenni d ayi izeddɣen.   
\m
\v 21 Xenni ttafeɣ ict n ccariɛa tenni tusa-dd ak-d tnefsect inu, tenni ixsen ad igg tcuni, am yudes ayi-dd řɣar.  
\v 22 Minzi farḥeɣ s Ccariɛa n AREBBI zi jjihet n bnadem nni iǧan di daxeř inu, \x ◘ \xo 7:22 \xt Afa. 3:16. \x*  
\v 23 maca ttwařiɣ din ccariɛa nneɣni deg iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* inu, tᵉttmenɣa ak-d ccariɛa n řeɛqeř inu uca tḥebbes ayi s ccariɛa n ddenb tenni iǧan deg iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* inu. \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt Gal. 5:17. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 24 Ayeḥḥat mana wemcum-a n bnadem i ǧiɣ! Wi d ayi ɣa issnejmen zi arrimet-a n řmewt?   
\m
\v 25 Ttqadiɣ AREBBI, \add wenni i d ayi issenjmen\add* s ufus n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ!  
\b  
\m Ammu aqa necc simant inu s řeɛqeř i xeddmeɣ i Ccariɛa n AREBBI, maca deg weysum inu i ccariɛa n ddenb.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 8
\s1 Tudart s Arruḥ Iqeddsen  
\m
\v 1 Xenni war dinni bu řḥukm x yinni igguren war iǧi \add ɛad\add* deg weysum s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.  
\v 2 Minzi Ccariɛa n Arruḥ n Tudart di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, aqa tfekk ac zi Ccariɛa n ddenb d řmewt. \x ◘ \xo 8:2 \xt Yḥ. 8:36; Rum. 6:18, 22; Gal. 5:1. \x*  
\v 3 Minzi maɣar tuɣa Ccariɛa teḍɛef s tuḍɛeft n weysum, issekk-dd AREBBI Mmis di ṣṣifet n weysum n ddenb x ssibbet n ddenb, maḥend ad iḥaseb ddenb deg weysum, \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Řex. 13:39; Rum. 3:28; Gal. 2:16; Ɛbr. 7:18. \x*  
\v 4 ḥima ad dayneɣ tᵉttwakemmeř tasegda n Ccariɛa, maḥend war neggur deg weysum, maca di Arruḥ.  
\v 5 Minzi inni iǧan deg weysum tteggen nneyyet nsen deg weysum, maca inni n Arruḥ tteggen nneyyet nsen di Arruḥ. \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt 1 Kur. 2:14. \x*  
\v 6 Minzi nneyyet n weysum d řmewt, maca nneyyet n Arruḥ d tudart d řehna.  
\v 7 Minzi nneyyet n weysum, aqa-tt d řeɛdawat i AREBBI, minzi war tᵉttegg ca array i Ccariɛa n AREBBI, maɣar war d as tzemmar.  
\v 8 Inni iǧan deg weysum war izemmaren ad arḍan AREBBI.   
\m
\v 9 Maca kenniw war teǧim ca deg weysum, maca di Arruḥ mařa izdeɣ daywem Arruḥ n AREBBI. Maca mařa ḥed war ɣares bu Arruḥ n Lmasiḥ, d wenni war ittiři nnes. \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt 1 Kur. 3:16. \x*  
\v 10 Mařa daywem Lmasiḥ, aqa arrimet temmut zi ssibbet n ddnub, maca Arruḥ iddar zi ssibbet n tsegda.  
\v 11 Mařa izdeɣ daywem Arruḥ n wenni dd-issnekkaren Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ zi taddart n imettinen, aqa wenni dd-issnekkaren Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ zi taddart n imettinen ad isseddar ɛawed arrimat nwem ifennan s Arruḥ nnes i izeddɣen daywem. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Rum. 6:4, 5; 1 Kur. 6:14; 2 Kur. 4:14; Afa. 2:5; Kul. 2:13. \x*   
\m
\v 12 Xenni, \add a\add* aytma, aqa aneɣ s umarwas, \add maca\add* war iǧi i weysum, ḥima ad neddar x řeḥsab n weysum,  
\v 13 minzi mařa teddarem x řeḥsab n weysum, ad temtem. Maca mařa tᵉttarrim ad mmtent řexdayem n arrimet s Arruḥ, ad teddarem.  
\v 14 Minzi marra inni ittwanedhen s Arruḥ n AREBBI, nitni d arrawen n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:14 \xt Gal. 5:18. \x*  
\v 15 Minzi kenniw war teksim ca arruḥ n tesmuɣi \add wenni kenniw i ɣa yarren d isemɣan\add*, ḥima ad teggʷedem ɛawed, maca aqa teksim Arruḥ i zi nettwaqbeř d arrawen, i zi nettřaɣa: ‘Tababat, Babatneɣ!’ \x ◘ \xo 8:15 \xt Ica. 56:5; 1 Kur. 2:12; Gal. 3:26; 4:5, 6; 2 Tim. 1:7. \x*  
\v 16 Arruḥ nni simant nnes icehhed ak-d arruḥ nneɣ, belli neccin d arrawen n AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt 2 Kur. 1:22; 5:5; Afa. 1:13; 4:30. \x*  
\v 17 Mařa neccin d arrawen, aqa aneɣ ɛawed d iwriten, iwriten n AREBBI d iwriten ak-d Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, maɣar mařa nweddeb akides, ad nettwaɛuǧi akides ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt 2 Tim. 2:11, 12. \x*   
\m
\v 18 Necc ttwassqenɛeɣ belli aweddeb i xaneɣ ittekken iḍa, war isdiheǧ ca ad ittwaɛbar s uɛuǧi i dd ɣa ittwasseḍharen dayneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 8:18 \xt Mt. 5:12; 2 Kur. 4:10, 17; Fil. 3:20; 1 Bṭ. 4:13; 1 Yḥ. 3:1, 2. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen ixezzar s usitem d uraji ɣar usargeb n warrawen n AREBBI.  
\v 20 Minzi marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen aqa ittwagg di řbaṭeř, war iǧi s řxaḍar, maca s wenni t iggin di řbaṭeř  
\v 21 s usitem belli marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen ad ittwafekk ɛawed zi tesmuɣi i řɣecc ɣar tiřelli n uɛuǧi n warrawen n AREBBI.  
\v 22 Aqa nessen belli marra min dd-ittwaxeřqen izehhar jmiɛ s unezbar n tarwa ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt Asa. 5:13\x*   
\m
\v 23 War iǧi nitni waha, maca uřa d neccin, inni ɣar teǧa dayneɣ \add řɣiǧet\add* tamezwarut n Arruḥ, nzehhar deg ixef nneɣ, nettraja ad nettwaqbeř d mmis, uřa d afekki n arrimat nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 8:23 \xt Lk. 21:28. \x*  
\v 24 S uyenni neddar deg usitem nni. Maca asitem ittbanen war iǧi d asitem, minzi min ittbanen i ḥed, mammec ɣa yegg ad dayes issitem ɛad?  
\v 25 Maca mařa nessittim di min war nettwiři, aqa nettraja t s ṣṣbar.  
\v 26 Di man aya ittɛawan aneɣ Arruḥ ɛawed di teḍɛeft nneɣ, minzi war nessin ca mammec d aneɣ i ɣa icuwwar ad neẓẓaǧ, maca Arruḥ simant nnes ittẓaǧa di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ s zzhir war ineṭqen. \x ◘ \xo 8:26 \xt Mt. 20:22; Yaɛ. 4:3. \x*   
\m
\v 27 Maca wenni ittbeqqcen deg wuřawen issen min iǧan d nneyyet n Arruḥ, aqa ittẓaǧa di ṭṭweɛ n imqeddasen am mammec t ixs AREBBI.  
\v 28 Neccin nessen aqa Netta iɛawen di kuřci i řxar i yinni ittexsen AREBBI, inni iɛeǧem i-ten qbeř maḥend ad ttwařaɣan.  
\v 29 Minzi inni izwar issen i-ten, aqa izwar iɛeǧem i-ten ḥima ad arwesen di ṣṣifet n Mmis, ḥima ad yiři Netta d Amenzu jar waṭṭas n wawmaten. \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Kul. 1:18. \x*  
\v 30 Uca inni Netta izzar iɛeǧem i-ten, aqa d inni x d iřaɣa ɛawed, u inni x d iřaɣa, aqa d inni isegged ɛawed, u inni isegged aqa d inni issɛuǧa ɛawed.   
\b  
\m
\v 31 Min ɣa nini xenni di man aya? Mařa AREBBI akidneɣ wi d aneɣ i ɣa iḍadden? \x ◘ \xo 8:31 \xt Řxř. 14:8. \x*  
\v 32 Wenni war iceṭṭaren ca x Mmis, maca iwca i-t di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ marra, mammec war d aneɣ ittic kuřci ak-d Mmis ɛawed? \x ◘ \xo 8:32 \xt Amz. 22:12; Ica. 53:5; Yḥ. 3:16. \x*  
\v 33 Wi ɣa iksin tanfuč i yinni ittwafarzen zi AREBBI? AREBBI d wenni ittseggaden. \x ◘ \xo 8:33 \xt Ica. 50:8. \x*  
\v 34 Wi ɣa iqḍan řḥukm? Lmasiḥ immut u ikkar-dd u Netta \add iqqim\add* ɣar ufusi n AREBBI, ittẓaǧa i neccin. \x ◘ \xo 8:34 \xt Ɛbr. 7:25. \x*  
\v 35 Min d ayi ɣa ibḍan x tayri n Lmasiḥ? Ma řmeḥnet, niɣ řḥebs, niɣ adarrec, niɣ řaẓ, niɣ tuɛaryent, niɣ lxaṭar, niɣ ssif?  
\v 36 Am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa x ssibbet nnec nettmetta kuř ass,\qt*  
\m \qt nettwaḥseb am iḥuřiyyen i tɣarṣt.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 8:36 \xt Izhd. 44:23; 1 Kur. 4:9; 2 Kur. 4:11. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 37 Maca di man aya marra nedweř zeg inni iɣellaben s Wenni d aneɣ ixsen.  
\v 38 Aqa necc ttwassqenɛeɣ belli niɣ řmewt, niɣ tudart, niɣ lmalakat, niɣ řḥukkam, niɣ ṣṣulaṭat, niɣ min n yiḍa, niɣ min i dd ɣa yasen,  
\v 39 niɣ řuɛřa, niɣ raǧaɣ, niɣ uřa d ict n řḥajjet nneɣni zi min dd-ittwaxeřqen, tzemmar ad aneɣ tebḍa x tayri n AREBBI, tenni di Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 9
\s1 Arebbi d řgens nnes Israil  
\m
\v 1 Qqareɣ tidett di Lmasiḥ, war ssxarriqeɣ ca, uca tanefsect inu tcehhed dayi s Arruḥ Iqeddsen, \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt Rum. 1:9; 2 Kur. 1:23; 11:31; Gal. 1:20; Fil. 1:8; 1 Ts. 2:5; 5:27. \x*  
\v 2 belli ɣari acḍan imɣar d řeḥriq war ittbeddi deg wuř inu.  
\v 3 Tuɣa ttẓaǧiɣ meɛlik ufiɣ ttwaḥarrmeɣ \add di mummu inu\add* x Lmasiḥ \add s ict nneɛřet\add* di ṭṭweɛ n wawmaten inu, řaǧ inu zi jjihet n weysum \add n arrimet\add*. \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Uf. 32:32; Rum. 10:1. \x*  
\v 4 arrawen n Israil, inni ittwaqebřen d mmis. Ɣarsen i yeǧa uɛuǧi, řɛuhud, Ccariɛa, tasexxart \add i iǧan di Zzawect Iqeddsen\add* i ɣares dd-iqqnen, lwuɛud d řejdud. \x ◘ \xo 9:4 \xt Uf. 4:22; Aɛwd. 7:6; Rum. 2:17; 3:2; Afa. 2:12. \x*  
\v 5 Zzaysen i dd-iban Lmasiḥ x webrid n weysum \add n arrimet\add* wenni d AREBBI x marra. I Netta i ɣa yiři \add marra\add* asemɣar d \add marra\add* lbaraka i řebda qaɛ. Amin! \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt Irm. 23:6; Yḥ. 1:1; Řex. 20:28; Rum. 1:4; Ɛbr. 1:8, 9, 10. \x*   
\m
\v 6 Maca war iǧi ařami awař n AREBBI war yiwiḍ, minzi marra inni zi Israil war ǧin ca d Israil. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Řxř. 23:19; Yḥ. 8:39; Rum. 2:28; 3:3; 2 Tim. 2:13. \x*  
\v 7 Uca uřa d marra nitni war ǧin ca d tarwa n Ibrahim, minzi nitni zi zzariɛet n Ibrahim, minzi ittwanna: “Di Isḥaq ad ac řaɣan zzariɛet.” \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Amz. 21:12; Gal. 3:29; 4:23; Ɛbr. 11:18. \x*  
\v 8 Man aya war ixs ad yini aqa tarwa ɛlaḥṣab jjadira n arrimet aqa-ten d tarwa n AREBBI, maca tarwa n lwaɛd ad ttwaḥesben d zzariɛet. \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Gal. 4:28. \x*  
\v 9 Minzi awař n lwaɛd d wa:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ɣar řweqt-a ad dd-aseɣ\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ɣares yiři ɣar Sara mmis!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Amz. 18:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Man aya war iǧi waha di tmesřact n Sara, maca uřa \add di tmesřact n\add* Rifqa, umi tmun ak-d uyenni n bnadem nni, jedditeɣ Isḥaq, \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt Amz. 25:21. \x*  
\v 11 tuɣa tizzar tettwassen řixḍaret n AREBBI umi tuɣa ɛad war dd-xřiqen iḥenjiren nnes, war zemmaren ad ggen \add ɛad\add* řxar niɣ řɣar, ḥima war tᵉttiři tmesřact deg webrid n řexdayem, maca deg webrid n wenni ittřaɣan.  
\v 12 Maɣar ittwanna \add i Rifqa\add*:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa ameqqran ad isexxar i umeẓyan!”,\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:12 \xt Amz. 25:23. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Yaɛqub i xseɣ, maca carheɣ Isu.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:13 \xt Mal. 1:2-3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Min ɣa nini xenni? Ma iqedd ad yiři ɣar AREBBI min war iseggden? Ɛemmarṣ! \x ◘ \xo 9:14 \xt Aɛwd. 32:4; 2 Im. 19:7; Ayub 34:10. \x*  
\v 15 Xzar, Netta inna ɛawed i Musa:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad areḥmeɣ wi xseɣ ad areḥmeɣ,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ḥinneɣ x wi xseɣ ad ḥinneɣ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt Uf. 33:19. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Xenni tamesřact war teqqim ca ɣar wi ittexsen uřa ɣar wi ittazzřen, maca ɣar AREBBI wenni yareḥḥmen.  
\v 17 Minzi ɛlaḥsab Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* inna Netta i firɛun:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa i man aya ssnekkareɣ-dd cek,\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima ad zzayek ssecneɣ jjehd inu,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ittwabarreḥ Isem inu\qt*  
\m \qt di marra ddunect.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:17 \xt Uf. 9:16. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 18 Xenni Netta ad yarḥem wi ixs, uca ad isseqseḥ wi ixs.   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Iwa, ad taɣ ad tinid: Mayemmi ittcetca ɛad, minzi wi ɣa immɛařan ak-d min ixs Netta?  
\v 20 Maca min teɛnid cek, a bnadem, wenni ittqacaḥen AREBBI? Ma min ittwaggen izemmar ad ini i wenni t iggin: “Mayemmi d ayi teggid ammu?” \x ◘ \xo 9:20 \xt Ica. 29:16, 45:9; Irm. 18:6. \x*  
\v 21 Ma war iǧi ɣar bu-třaxt ṣṣulṭa x třaxt ḥima ad igg \add zeg ict n řɛejnet\add* ict n řqecɛet i lkarama u wenneɣni i ubehdeř? \x ◘ \xo 9:21 \xt Irm. 18:4-6; 2 Tim. 2:20. \x*  
\v 22 Maɣar AREBBI, \add wenni\add* tuɣa ixs ad isscen aɣḍab nnes d jjehd nnes, issiweḍ lɣaḍab nnes s waṭṭas n ttasiɛ n řxaḍar x řeqcuɛ n weɣḍab inni ittwasswejden marra i uhellek,  
\v 23 uca ifarɣ tayri nnes x řeqcuɛ n arreḥmet inni izwar issewjed i-ten i uɛuǧi i AREBBI!  
\v 24 Maɣar neccin d inni ittwařaɣan, war iǧi zeg Wudayen waha, maca ɛawed zi řegnus.  
\v 25 Am mammec ittwanna ɛawed di Ḥuciɛa:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad semmiɣ i yinni war iǧin d řgens inu\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Řgens inu!’,\qt*  
\m \qt uca i yinni war iǧin d amɛizz d ‘Amɛizz!’”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:25 \xt Ḥuc. 2:25 \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 26 Ad yiři deg wemcan mani d asen ittwařaɣa:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘War iǧi d řgens inu!’,\qt*  
\b  
\m belli dinni ad asen řaɣan:  
\b  
\m \qt ‘Arrawen n AREBBI iddaren!’\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:26 \xt Ḥuc. 2:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 27 Maca Icaɛya ibarreḥ zi jjihet n ayt n Israil:  
\b  
\m \qt “Mařa tuɣa řqedd n ayt n Israil\qt*  
\m \qt anect n ijdi n řebḥar,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl mɣir\+tl* min i ɣa iqqimen ad injem.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:27 \xt Ica. 10:22. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 \qt “Tamesřact tbedd nican u ad tᵉttwaqfeř,\qt*  
\m \qt SIDI ad tt igg x temmurt.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:28 \xt Ica. 10:22, 23. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 29 Am mammec izwar Icaɛya inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Maɛlik SIDI n řɛeskarat war d aneɣ ijji\qt*  
\m \qt inni iqqimen ddaren,\qt*  
\m \qt iři nedweř am Sadum u narwes di Ɛamurra.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:29 \xt Amz. 19:24; Ica. 1:9; 13:19; Irm. 50:40; Ḥiz. 16:46. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 30 Min ɣa nini xenni? Ma xenni řegnus inni war yarezzun tasegda, aqa ksin tasegda? Iwa, maca tasegda tenni s l’iman.  
\v 31 Maca Israil nni iḍeffaren Ccariɛa n tsegda, war yiwiḍ ca ɣar Ccariɛa n tsegda. \x ◘ \xo 9:31 \xt Rum. 10:2; 11:7. \x*  
\v 32 Mayemmi? Minzi \add tasegda\add* nni war teǧi ca zi l’iman maca zi řexdayem n Ccariɛa, minzi nitni nderfen deg Weẓru n unedref, \x ◘ \xo 9:32 \xt Ica. 8:14; 1 Bṭ. 2:7\x*  
\v 33 am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa ad ggeɣ di Ṣihyun Aẓru i unedref\qt*  
\m \qt d Weẓru i uneqrad.\qt*  
\m \qt Marra wi zzayes i ɣa yamnen,\qt*  
\m \qt war ittseḍḥa.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 9:33 \xt Izhd. 2:12; 118:22; Awřn. 16:20; Ica. 8:14; 28:16; Irm. 17:7; Mt. 21:42; 1 Bṭ. 2:6. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 10
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* aytma, ameẓri n wuř inu u taẓaǧit tenni ẓuǧeɣ ɣar AREBBI di ṭṭweɛ n \add Israil\add*, aqa-tt ḥima ad ɣarsen tiři Tudart.  
\v 2 Aqa cehhdeɣ xasen aqa nitni ɣarsen cḍaret i AREBBI, maca břa tussna. \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt Řex. 22:3; Rum. 9:31; Gal. 4:17. \x*  
\v 3 Maɣar war ssinen tasegda n AREBBI, maca arezzun ad ṭṭfen di tsegda n ixef nsen. S uya war sswaḍɛen ixef nsen i tsegda n AREBBI.  
\v 4 Minzi akemmeř n Ccariɛa netta d Lmasiḥ i tsegda i kuř ijjen i ittamnen. \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Mt. 5:17; Řex. 13:38; 2 Kur. 3:13; Gal. 3:24. \x*  
\v 5 Minzi Musa yura zi jjihet n tsegda di Ccariɛa:  
\b  
\m \qt “Wenni itteggen man aya,\qt*  
\m \qt ad zzayes iddar.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt Lawi 18:5; Ḥiz. 20:11; Gal. 3:12. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 6 Maca tasegda tenni zi l’iman teqqar ammu:  
\b  
\m \qt “War teqqar deg wuř nnec:\qt*  
\m \qt ‘Wi ɣa igaɛɛden ɣar ujenna\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad issehwa Lmasiḥ?”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 7 niɣ:  
\b  
\m \qt “Wi dd-ihwan deg weḥfur n řaxart,\qt*  
\m \qt uca issgeɛɛed Lmasiḥ\qt*  
\m \qt zi taddart n imettinen?”\qt*   
\b  
\m
\v 8 Maca min ixs ad yini man aya \add xenni\add*?  
\b  
\m \qt “Tamwarrit tudes i cek,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa-t deg uqemmum nnec uřa deg wuř nnec.\qt*  
\m \qt Wa d Awař n l’iman i zi nettbarreḥ.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt Aɛwd. 30:12-14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Mařa tcehded i Siditneɣ Yasuɛ s uqemmum nnec uca ad tamned s wuř nnec belli AREBBI issnekkar i-t zi taddart n imettinen, ad teddared.  
\v 10 Minzi uř i dayes ittamen ad ittwasegged, uca aqemmum i zzayes icehhden, ad iddar.  
\v 11 Minzi Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* qqarent:  
\b  
\m \qt “Marra wi zzayes i ɣa yamnen,\qt*  
\m \qt war ittseḍḥi ca.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:11 \xt Ica. 28:16; Rum. 9:33. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Minzi Netta war ittegg bu řfarz jar Wudayen d Iramiyyen, minzi Netta d Ijjen, SIDI nsen marra nni ittenfeyyaḍ řxar x marra inni xas dd-ittřaɣan. \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Řex. 15:9; Rum. 3:22. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 \qt “Minzi kuř ijjen\qt*  
\m \qt wenni i ɣa iřaɣan s Yisem n SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt ad iddar.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Yuw. 3:5; Řex. 2:21. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 14 Mammec i ɣa řaɣan x Wenni di war uminen ca? Niɣ mammec ɣa yamnen deg Wenni mixef war sřin, niɣ mammec ɣa sřen, mařa uřa d ijj war zzayes ibarreḥ ca?  
\v 15 Mammec i ɣa barrḥen mařa war dd-ttwassekken? Am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Mecḥař ḍarfen iḍaren\qt*  
\m \qt n yinni ittbarrḥen s řehna,\qt*  
\m \qt n yinni ittbarrḥen s tebratin tiṣebḥanin.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:15 \xt Ica. 52:7; Nḥm. 2:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 16 Maca war iǧi marra ṭṭaɛen i ubarreḥ n Řexbar Aṣebḥan n L’Injil, minzi Icaɛya iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “\+tl A\+tl* Sidi inu, wi ɣa yamnen di tebrat nneɣ?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt Ica. 53:1; Yḥ. 12:38. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Aqa l’iman zeg usḥessi uca asḥessi zeg Wawař n AREBBI.  
\v 18 Maca ad iniɣ:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ma zeɛma nitni war sřin?”\qt*,  
\b  
\m \qt “Xzar, řḥess nsen iffeɣ-dd\qt*  
\m \qt ɣar marra tammurt,\qt*  
\m \qt uca awařen nsen ɣar tneggura n ddunect.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Izhd. 19:5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 19 Maca ad iniɣ:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ma Israil war tefhim ca man aya?”\qt*  
\b  
\m Ɣar umezwar Musa inna:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad daywem ggeɣ tusmi\qt*  
\m \qt zeg ijj n řgens i war iǧin ca d řgens,\qt*  
\m \qt uca s yijj n řgens i war ittᵉṭṭiɛen\qt*  
\m \qt ad daywem ggeɣ axeyyeq.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt Aɛwd. 32:21. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 20 Uca Icaɛya izɛem ad yini:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa baneɣ-dd i yinni war xafi yarezzun,\qt*  
\m \qt aqa ufin ayi inni war xafi isseqsan.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Ica. 65:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Maca zi jjihet n Israil iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ass ikmeř sswiẓẓḍeɣ ifassen inu\qt*  
\m \qt i ijj n řgens ittɛekksen, iɛeṣṣan.”\qt*\x ◘ \xo 10:21 \xt Ica. 65:2. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 11
\s1 Min iqqimen n Israil d řefruɛ iřeqqmen  
\m
\v 1 Maca necc ad iniɣ: Ma yugi AREBBI xenni řgens nnes? Ɛemmarṣ! Aqa necc simant inu ɛawed d ijj n weryaz zi Israil, zi zzariɛet n Ibrahim, zi teqbič n Binyamin. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Irm. 31:37; 2 Kur. 11:22; Fil. 3:5. \x*  
\v 2 AREBBI war ineṭṭar ca řgens nnes i tuɣa issen zeg umezwaru. Niɣ war tessinem ca min iqqar Wedlis \add Iqeddsen\add* x Iliya, am mammec tuɣa iksi tanfuč x Israil ɣar AREBBI, inna:   
\b  
\m
\v 3 \qt “A Sidi, nɣin inabiyyen nnec,\qt*  
\m \qt areddǧen iɛalṭaren nnec.\qt*  
\m \qt Qqimeɣ necc waha,\qt*  
\m \qt uca nitni arezzun řeɛmar inu.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:3 \xt 1 Ij. 19:10, 14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Ittwanna as s ijj n řewḥiy:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa jjiɣ i yixef inu sebɛa-ařaf n yeryazen,\qt*  
\m \qt inni war ḍrin ca ɣar iḍaren zzat i Baɛal,\qt*  
\m \qt war ɛebden i Baɛal.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:4 \xt 1 Ij. 19:18. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 5 Ammu di řweqt n yiḍa ɛawed, aqa iqqim yijj n řbaqi am t ixḍar Netta x řeḥsab n arḍa. \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Rum. 9:27. \x*  
\v 6 Mařa teǧa s arḍa, aqa war tᵉttiři ɛad s řexdayem, niɣ xenni arḍa war iǧi ɛad d arḍa. Maca mařa s řexdayem, war teǧi ɛad d arḍa. Mařa lla, aqa řxedmet war teǧi ɛad d řxedmet. \x ◘ \xo 11:6 \xt Aɛwd. 9:4. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Min ɣa nini xenni? Min tuɣa tarezzu Israil war t tᵉṭṭif, maca inni ittwafarzen ṭṭfen t uca inneɣni dewřen d idarɣařen deg wuřawen nsen, \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt Rum. 9:31. \x*  
\v 8 am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Aqa AREBBI iwca asen arruḥ iḍbaren\qt*  
\m \qt d tiṭṭawin i war ittwiřin,\qt*  
\m \qt d imezzuɣen i war ittesřin,\qt*  
\m \qt ař ass n yiḍa.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:8 \xt Aɛwd. 29:2; Ica. 6:9-10; 29:10; Ḥiz. 12:2; Mt. 13:14; Mk. 4:12; Lk. 8:10; Yḥ. 12:40; Řex. 28:26. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Dawud inna ɛawed:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad tedweř tazewḍa \+tl n tiɣarṣin\+tl* nsen\qt*  
\m \qt d řfex i nitni,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad tedweř řmunet nsen d tɛenkrift.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:9 \xt Izhd. 69:23. \x*   
\m
\v 10 \qt Ejj ad darɣřent tiṭṭawin nsen\qt*  
\m \qt ḥima war ttwiřin nitni,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ejj ad qewsen iɛurar nsen i řebda.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt Izhd. 69:23-24. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Maca necc ad iniɣ \add xenni\add*: Ma nderfen, maɣar ittxeṣṣa ad wḍan? Ɛemmarṣ! Maca s uweṭṭu nsen tiweḍ-dd Tudart i řegnus, ḥima ad dewřen ttasmen.  
\v 12 Mařa idweř unedref nsen d agřa d ameqqran i ddunect uca řḥukm xasen d agřa i řegnus, mecḥař qaɛ i ɣa yiweḍ uɛemmar nsen d afeyyeḍ.  
\v 13 Aqa ssawařeɣ akidwem, \add a\add* řegnus, necc d wenni d rrasul i řegnus, aqa ttssemɣareɣ di řxedmet n tsexxart inu: \f ◼ \fr 11:13 \ft \+fk rrasul\ft  - niɣ ‘amazan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:13 \xt Řex. 9:15; 13:2; 22:21; Gal. 1:16; 2:8; Afa. 3:8; 1 Tim. 2:7; 2 Tim. 1:11. \x*  
\v 14 Ad taɣ ad zemmareɣ ad ssekkareɣ tusmi deg ayt n řgens inu uca ad ssnejmeɣ ca zzaysen.  
\v 15 Iwa, mařa amenḍar nsen aqa-t d aṣřaḥ i ddunect, mammec ɣa yiři wedwař nsen mɣir d Tudart zi taddart n imettinen!  
\v 16 Mařa tuɣa tamezwarut \add n ṣṣabet\add* tqeddes, amenni uřa d řɛejnet \add n arecti\add* tqeddes! Mařa tuɣa aẓwar iqeddes, amenni uřa d řefruɛ. \x ◘ \xo 11:16 \xt Řxř. 15:20\x*  
\v 17 Uca mařa ttwaqessen ca n řefruɛ u \add xenni\add* cek, am yijj n uzemmur n řexřa, tᵉttwařeqqmed deg wemcan nsen, tdewřed tnefɛed zeg iẓewran d zzect n tzitunt,  
\v 18 war tuff ca x řefruɛ. Mařa tuffed, \add ssen\add*, aqa cek war teksid ca aẓwar, maca aẓwar iksi cek.   
\m
\v 19 Ad taɣ ad tinid: “Aqa ttwaqessen řefruɛ, ḥima necc ad ttwařeqqmeɣ.”  
\v 20 Iwa, nitni ttwaqessen zi ssibbet n břa l’iman nsen, uca cek s l’iman \add tᵉttwařeqqmed uca\add* teksid \add amcan nsen\add*. War tuff ca, maca ggʷed.  
\v 21 Minzi mařa tuɣa AREBBI war ittceṭṭar ca x řefruɛ n ṭṭbiɛet, war xak ittceṭṭar ca ɛawed.  
\v 22 Aqa da d řeḍrafet n AREBBI d řewɛaret nnes: řewɛaret x yinni iwḍan, maca řeḍrafet xak mařa tᵉṭṭfed di řeḍrafet nnes, niɣ uřa d cek ad tᵉttwaqessed.  
\v 23 Uřa d nitni ad ttwařeqqmen, mařa war qqimen di tikkest n l’iman nsen, minzi ɣar AREBBI tizemmar, ḥima ad ten iřeqqem ɛawed. \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt 2 Kur. 3:16. \x*  
\v 24 Minzi mařa cek, wenni iǧan s ṭṭbiɛet d ijj n uzemmur n řexřa, tᵉttwaqessed uca tᵉttwařeqqmed di tzitunt taṣebḥant, mecḥař ihewnen ktar ad ttwařeqqmen nitni di tzitunt nni dd-ittasen ak-d ṭṭbiɛet nsen!   
\b  
\m
\v 25 Minzi ttexseɣ ad tessnem ssirr-a, \add a\add* aytma, ḥima war ttiřim d imiɣisen ak-d yixef nwem, aqa temsar ict n usdaɣeř n wuř x Israil i drus n řweqt ař dd ɣa yadef uɛemmar n řegnus, \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Lk. 21:24. \x*  
\v 26 uca xenni marra Israil ad tedweř ɣar Tudart am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Amsenjem ad dd-iffeɣ zi Ṣihyun\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad issbeɛɛed řmuɛṣiyyet x Yaɛqub.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt Izhd. 14:7; Ica. 27:9; 59:20; Irm. 31:31, 32, 33, 34; 2 Kur. 3:16; Ɛbr. 8:8; 10:16. \x*   
\m
\v 27 \qt ”Xenni ad ṭṭfen di Řɛahd\qt*  
\m \qt i dd-yusin Zzayi,\qt*  
\m \qt x minni i ɣa ɣfareɣ i ddnub nsen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:27 \xt Ica. 59:20, 21; Dan. 9:24\x*   
\b  
\m
\v 28 Zi jjihet n L’Injil nitni aqa d řɛedyan di ṭṭweɛ nwem, maca zi jjihet n řixḍaret \add i zi ttwaxḍaren nitni\add*, aqa nitni d imɛizzen x ssibbet n řejdud.  
\v 29 Minzi AREBBI war ittbeddař tawhibt nnes \add n arḍa\add* uřa d třaɣit nnes.  
\v 30 Minzi am mammec tuɣa kenniw zic war tᵉṭṭiɛem ca AREBBI, maca řexxu aqa teksim arreḥmet s řmuɛṣiyyet nsen,  
\v 31 ammu nitni ɛawed war ṭṭiɛen ca řexxu i arreḥmet tenni xawem \add dd-yusin\add*, ḥima ad xasen dd-tas arreḥmet.  
\v 32 Minzi AREBBI iḥebbes i-ten marra sadu řmuɛṣiyyet, ḥima ad ten yarḥem marra. \x ◘ \xo 11:32 \xt Gal. 3:22. \x*   
\m
\v 33 A, raǧaɣ n wagřa d tiɣit d tussna n AREBBI, mammec ɣa yegg bnadem ad iqeǧeb řeḥkamat nnes, mammec ɣa yegg ad yaf ibriden nnes.   
\b  
\m
\v 34 \qt “Minzi wi ɣa issnen nneyyet n SIDI?”\qt*  
\m niɣ:  
\m \qt “Wi d as iǧan d amcawar?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:34 \xt Ica. 40:13; 1 Kur. 2:16. \x*   
\m
\v 35 niɣ:  
\m \qt “Wi d as izzaren iwca as \+tl ca\+tl*,\qt*  
\m \qt umi d as ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaxeǧeṣ zzayes?”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 11:35 \xt Ayub 41:3. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 36 Minzi marra zzayes i iǧa, u marra dayes, u marra aqa-t s ufus nnes. I Netta i ɣa yiři \add marra\add* asemɣar d \add marra\add* lbaraka i řebda qaɛ. Amin! \x ◘ \xo 11:36 \xt Awřn. 16:4; 1 Kur. 8:6. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 12
\s1 Tiɣarṣa iddaren  
\m
\v 1 X uyenni ttřaɣiɣ kenniw, \add a\add* aytma, s arreḥmet tameqqrant n AREBBI, ad tqeddmem arrimat nwem d taɣarṣt iddaren, iqeddsen, yarḍan i AREBBI, wa d aɛbad nwem icuwwaren. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt Rum. 6:13, 16; 1 Bṭ. 2:5. \x*  
\v 2 War temquddam ak-d ddunect-a, maca beddřem s uřeqqem n řeɛqeř nwem zi jdid, ḥima ad tqeǧbem min ixs AREBBI: min icnan d min yarḍan d min ikemmřen. \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt Afa. 5:17; 1 Ts. 4:3; 1 Yḥ. 2:15. \x*   
\m
\v 3 Aqa s arḍa tenni d ayi immewcen, qqareɣ awem marra: war ttxarriṣem sennej i min ittřiq uxarraṣ nnes, maca xarrṣem nican ɛlaḥsab řqedd n l’iman i iwca AREBBI i kuř ijjen \add zzaywem\add*. \x ◘ \xo 12:3 \xt Rum. 1:5; 1 Kur. 12:11; Afa. 4:7. \x*  
\v 4 Am mammec ɣarneɣ aṭṭas n iɣezdisen deg ict n arrimet uca marra iɣezdisen \add n arrimet\add* war ɣarsen bu řxedmet d icten, \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt 1 Kur. 12:27; Afa. 1:23; 4:16; 5:23; Kul. 1:24. \x*  
\v 5 ammu neccin, waxxa d aṭṭas, aqa aneɣ d ict n Arrimet di Lmasiḥ d iɣezdisen ijjen i wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 12:5 \xt 1 Kur. 12:4; 2 Kur. 10:13; 1 Bṭ. 4:10. \x*  
\v 6 Maca ɣarneɣ tiwhibin immsebḍan ɛlaḥsab arḍa i d aneɣ immewcen: \add ijjen ɣares tawhibt\add* maḥend ad inebb ɛlaḥsab řqedd n l’iman, \x ◘ \xo 12:6 \xt 1 Kur. 12:4. \x*  
\v 7 wenneɣni ɣares nneyyet n tsexxart maḥend ad isexxar, niɣ \add tawhibt\add* n umseɣɣar maḥend ad issɣar, \x ◘ \xo 12:7 \xt 1 Kur. 12:10; 1 Bṭ. 4:10, 11. \x*  
\v 8 \add niɣ tawhibt n\add* usfewwej maḥend ad issfewwej, \add niɣ tawhibt\add* maḥend ad iwc s tecrimet, \add niɣ tawhibt n\add* uḍebbar s wemḥaḍ, \add niɣ tawhibt n\add* arreḥmet s řefraḥet. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Aɛwd. 15:7; Mt. 6:1, 2, 3; 2 Kur. 9:7. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 9 Ad tiři tayri nwem břa nnifaq. Carhem řɣar, tcebbarem di min icnan.  
\v 10 Iřim mliḥ ijjen ak-d tawmat nwem, xsem ijj i wenneɣni, izzarem ad tcennɛem ijjen wenneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 12:10 \xt Afa. 4:2; Fil. 2:3; 1 Bṭ. 5:5; Ɛbr. 13:1; 1 Bṭ. 1:22; 2:17. \x*  
\v 11 Iřim d imḥaḍen, war ttiřim d ifinyanen. Iřim d timessi di arruḥ, ɛebdem Siditwem,  
\v 12 Farḥem di min iǧan asitem nwem, di řmeḥnet nwem ṣbarem uca ṭṭfem řebda di tẓaǧit. \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt Lk. 18:1; Rum. 15:13; Afa. 6:18; Kul. 4:2; 1 Ts. 5:16, 17; Ɛbr. 10:36; 12:1; Yaɛ. 5:7\x*  
\v 13 Wcem afus di min iḥdajen imqeddasen. Ggem s řeḍrafet ak-d ibarraniyyen. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt 1 Kur. 16:1; Ɛbr. 13:2; 1 Bṭ. 4:9. \x*  
\v 14 Barkem inni kenniw imarrten, barkem war neɛɛřem ca. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Mt. 5:44; 1 Kur. 4:12. \x*  
\v 15 Farḥem ak-d inni ifarḥen, rum ak-d yinni ittrun.  
\v 16 Ḥesbem aytmatwem am mammec tḥessbem ixef nwem, War ttiřim d imɛeffaren, maca ruḥem ak-d imwaḍɛen. War ttiřim ca d imiɣisen ak-d yixef nwem. \x ◘ \xo 12:16 \xt Awřn. 3:7; Ica. 5:21; Rum. 15:5; 1 Kur. 1:10; Fil. 2:2; 3:16; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*  
\v 17 War ttarrim ca ḥed x řɣar s řɣar, maca ggem min icnan i marra iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 12:17 \xt Awřn. 20:22; Mt. 5:39; 1 Kur. 6:7; 2 Kur. 8:21; 1 Ts. 5:15; 1 Bṭ. 2:12. \x*  
\v 18 Mařa tzemmarem, mecḥař ma i dd-ittasen zzaywem, ṣeřḥem ak-d marra iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 12:18 \xt Mk. 9:50; Ɛbr. 12:14. \x*  
\v 19 War ttentiqimem ca i yixef nwem, \add a\add* imɛizzen, maca wcem amcan i weɣḍab, minzi tura: “Mařa kenniw war tarrim tasɣart s yixef nwem, Necc ad arreɣ tasɣart newem, iqqar AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt Aɛwd. 32:35; Mt. 5:39; Lk. 6:29; Ɛbr. 10:30. \x*   
\m
\v 20 Mařa iǧuẓ řeɛdu nwem, seccem t, mařa ifud, wcem as ad isu, minzi mařa teggid aya, ad tyarwed řefḥem itteḥduduqen x uzeǧif nnes. \x ◘ \xo 12:20 \xt Awřn. 25:21-22; Mt. 5:44. \x*  
\v 21 War ttejjim ca řɣar ad kenniw iɣřeb, maca ɣeřbem x řɣar s řxar.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 13
\s1 Awaḍeɛ i ṣṣulṭa  
\m
\v 1 Ejj kuř ijj ad iwaḍeɛ i ṣṣulaṭat inni iǧan s lɛaḍama, minzi war din ṣṣulṭa mɣir s AREBBI, uca ṣṣulaṭat tinni iǧan, aqa issbedd i-tent AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Awřn. 8:15; Dan. 4:29; Tit. 3:1; 1 Bṭ. 2:13. \x*  
\v 2 S uya wenni i ɣa immɛařan ak-d ṣṣulṭa, ittemɛařa ak-d min issbedd AREBBI, d yinni ittemɛařan ad ksin řḥukm nsen.  
\v 3 Minzi řquḍat war ǧin i tiggʷudi n yinni itteggen řxar, maca n yinni itteggen řɣar. Ma texsed ad tiřid břa tiggʷudi zi ṣṣulṭa \add n řquḍat\add*? Egg min icnan, ad ac yiři ccan zzayes,  
\v 4 minzi \add ṣṣulṭa\add* d tamsexxart n AREBBI i řefḍeř nnec. Maca mařa teggid řɣar, ggʷed, minzi \add ṣṣulṭa\add* war tbekkes ca ssif baṭeř umi nettat d tamsexxart n AREBBI, aqa tneqqem s weɣḍab iqesḥen x yinni itteggen řɣar.  
\v 5 S uya ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad neṭṭaɛ, war iǧi x ssibbet n weɣḍab waha, maca ɛawed x ssibbet n tnefsect.  
\v 6 X ssibbet-a tᵉttxeǧṣem ḍḍariba i kuř azeǧif umi nitni d imsexxaren n AREBBI i ittwaggen i man aya simant nnes. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt 1 Bṭ. 2:\x*  
\v 7 X uya, wcem i marra min d asen ittxeṣṣan: ḍḍariba i wenni umi dd-tusa ḍḍariba i kuř azeǧif, řexřaṣ i wenni umi dd-yusa řexřaṣ, aweqqar i wenni umi dd-yusa uweqqar, ccan i wenni isdaheǧen ccan.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Tayri d akemmeř n Ccariɛa  
\m
\v 8 War tteggem amarwas ɣar ḥed mɣir wenni n tayri ak-d wayawya, minzi wenni ittexsen wenni d as yudsen, aqa ikemmeř Ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 13:8 \xt Gal. 5:14; 1 Tim. 1:5. \x*  
\v 9 Minzi \add Ccariɛa\add* teqqar ɛawed: “War zenni, war neqq, war tticar, war ttasem!”, uca mařa din ca n tewṣeyyet nneɣni, aqa atent munent deg wawař-a: “Ad texsed jjar nnec am ixef nnec!” \x ◘ \xo 13:9 \xt Uf. 20:13-17; Lawi 19:18; Aɛwd. 5:17-19; Mt. 19:18; 22:39; Mk. 12:31; Gal. 5:14; Yaɛ. 2:8. \x*  
\v 10 Tayri war ttḍarri ca jjar. S uyenni tayri nettat d řekmař n Ccariɛa.   
\m
\v 11 Aqa ssneɣ aqa ta d řweqt d tsaɛɛet ḥima ad nfaq zeg iḍeṣ, minzi řexxu Tudart nneɣ tudes-dd ktar zeg wami nedweř numen. \x ◘ \xo 13:11 \xt Afa. 5:14; 1 Ts. 5:6. \x*  
\v 12 Řexxu teɛdu ǧiřet, yiweḍ-dd uziř. Ejj aneɣ ad nessars řexdayem n taǧest, ad neksi řesnaḥ n tfawt. \x ◘ \xo 13:12 \xt Kul. 3:8; 1 Ts. 5:5. \x*  
\v 13 Ejj aneɣ ad nuyur s ucuwwar axmi d aziř, war iǧi di zzhu abarcan, řa deg uɣelli, řa di texmuji n farq-ccɣeř di qama uřa deg umenɣi d řeḥsed, \x ◘ \xo 13:13 \xt Lk. 21:34; 1 Kur. 6:10; Afa. 5:5; Fil. 4:8; 1 Ts. 4:12; 5:6; Yaɛ. 3:14. \x*  
\v 14 maca arḍem Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, war tticem taynit i nnecwat n weysum nwem. \x ◘ \xo 13:14 \xt Gal. 3:27; 1 Bṭ. 2:11. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 14
\s1 Aqbař n wayawya  
\m
\v 1 Wi iḍeɛfen di l’iman, wcem as afus, war ttemsebḍam deg ixarriṣen nwem jar awem.  
\v 2 Aqa din ḥed yumen izemmar ad icc kuřci, maca wenni iḍeɛfen ad icc tibbi waha. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt Awřn. 15:7 \x*  
\v 3 Wenni ittetten, war isseḥqari wenni war ittetten, d wenni war ittetten, war iḥekkem x wenni ittetten, minzi AREBBI iqbeř i-t.  
\v 4 Min teɛnid cek wenni iḥekkmen x umsexxar n wenneɣni? Minzi mařa ibedd, d man aya i bab nnes, u mařa iwḍa, d man aya i bab nnes. Sides izemmar ad t issbedd d abeddi. \x ◘ \xo 14:4 \xt Yaɛ. 4:12. \x*   
\m
\v 5 Aqa din ḥed ittɣiř as aqa din ass sennej i wass nneɣni, u wenneɣni ittɣiř as aqa kuř ass kifkif. Ejj kuř ijjen ad iqneɛ di řbař nnes nican. \x ◘ \xo 14:5 \xt Gal. 4:10; Kul. 2:16. \x*  
\v 6 Wenni iweqqaren ijj n wass, i Sides i t ɣa iweqqar. Wenni war iweqqaren ass, i Sides i war t iweqqar. Wenni ittetten, ittett i Sides, minzi ad icekkar AREBBI. Wenni war ittetten ca, i Sides war ittett ca uca netta ad icekkar AREBBI \add ɛawed\add*. \x ◘ \xo 14:6 \xt 1 Kur. 10:31; 1 Tim. 4:3. \x*  
\v 7 Minzi uřa d ijj zzayneɣ aqa iddar i yixef nnes, uca uřa d ijjen immut i yixef nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:7 \xt 2 Kur. 5:15; Gal. 2:20; 1 Ts. 5:10; 1 Bṭ. 4:2. \x*  
\v 8 Minzi mařa neddar, ad neddar i Siditneɣ, niɣ mařa nemmut ad nemmet i Siditneɣ. S uya, ma neddar niɣ nemmut, aqa neccin i Siditneɣ.  
\v 9 Minzi i uya i immut Lmasiḥ, uca idweř iddar \add ɛawed\add* uca ikkar-dd, ḥima ad yiři d SIDI i yinni immuten uřa i yinni iddaren.  
\v 10 Maca cek, mayemmi ɣa tḥekmed x umac? Niɣ mayemmi ɛawed cek tesseḥqarad umac? Minzi neccin marra ad nbedd qibač i řkursi n ccreɛ n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt Mt. 25:31; 2 Kur. 5:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “S tidett, am ddareɣ Necc, iqqar SIDI,\qt*  
\m \qt ad ayi aḍaren marra ifadden\qt*  
\m \qt u kuř iřes ad xafi iched.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 14:11 \xt Ica. 45:23; 49:18 Fil. 2:10. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Xenni ejj kuř ijjen zzayneɣ ad igg řeḥsab x yixef nnes qibač i AREBBI. \x ◘ \xo 14:12 \xt Izhd. 62:13; Irm. 17:10; 32:19; Mt. 16:27; Rum. 2:6; 1 Kur. 3:8; 2 Kur. 5:10; Gal. 6:5; Asa. 2:23; 22:12. \x*  
\v 13 Zi řexxu d tsawent war ḥekkmem ijjen x wenneɣni, maca ḥsen ad teksed awař maḥend war tessarsed ca ijj n weẓru maḥend ad dayes inqarḍ umac. \x ◘ \xo 14:13 \xt 1 Kur. 10:32; 2 Kur. 6:3. \x*  
\v 14 Minzi necc ssneɣ, aqa ttwassqenɛeɣ di SIDI Yasuɛ, belli uřa d ict n řḥajjet texmej i Netta, mɣir i wenni tt iḥesben d řexmej, aqa i netta waha umi texmej. \x ◘ \xo 14:14 \xt Mt. 15:11; Mk. 17:17-23; Řex. 10:15; 1 Kur. 8:4; 1 Tim. 4:4. \x*  
\v 15 Mařa ixeyyeq umac x ssibbet n macca i teccid, aqa cek war tuyured di tayri. War tteḥḥi ca s macca nnec wenni i xef immut Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt 1 Kur. 8:11. \x*  
\v 16 Min nḥesseb d řxar i neccin, war ttejji ḥed ad xas issiweř s řɣar.  
\v 17 Minzi Tageldit n AREBBI war teǧi di macca d tissit, maca di tsegda d řehna d řefraḥet s Arruḥ Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 14:17 \xt 1 Kur. 8:8. \x*  
\v 18 Minzi wenni isexxaren i Lmasiḥ di man aya, aqa yarḍa AREBBI uca netta d ameqbuř ɣar iwdan.   
\m
\v 19 Ad neḍfar xenni min iǧan i řehna d řebni n ijjen i wenneɣni.  
\v 20 War ttareddeǧ ca řxedmet n AREBBI x ssibbet n macca. Marra timesřayin aqa atent d timezdag, maca uct x bnadem wenni i ɣa igg aẓru i unedref s macca nnes. \x ◘ \xo 14:20 \xt Tit. 1:15. \x*  
\v 21 Mliḥ umi war nᵉttett ca aysum u war nsess ca binu niɣ war nᵉttegg uřa d ict n řḥajjet i di i ɣa inderf umac. \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt 1 Kur. 8:13. \x*  
\v 22 Ma tᵉttwassqenɛed i yixef nnec? Ad ac yiři man aya i yixef nnec zzat i AREBBI. Sseɛd n wenni war ittikkwiḍ ccreɛ x yixef nnes di min d as ittɣiř mliḥ.  
\v 23 Maca wenni ittcekkan xmi ittett, ittwaḥaseb, minzi man aya war iǧi zi l’iman. Qaɛ min war iǧin zi l’iman, aqa-t d ddenb. \x ◘ \xo 14:23 \xt Tit. 1:15. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 15
\s1 Inni iḍeɛfen d inni ijehden  
\m
\v 1 Maca neccin inni ijehden, ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad narbu tuḍɛeft n yinni iḍeɛfen, war nettiwi ca arḍa i yixef nneɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt 1 Kur. 9:22; Gal. 6:1 \x*  
\v 2 Kuř ijjen ad issarḍa jjar nnes i tcuni d řebni.  
\v 3 Minzi Lmasiḥ ɛawed war issarḍi ca Ixef nnes, maca am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Tikkwura n yinni i Cek ikkwaren,\qt*  
\m \qt wḍant-i-dd xafi.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:3 \xt Izhd. 69:10; Ica. 53:4, 5. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 4 Minzi marra min tura zic, tura i useřmed nneɣ, ḥima s ṣṣbar d ucejjeɛ s min iǧan di Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* ad ɣarneɣ yiři usitem. \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt Rum. 4:23, 24. \x*  
\v 5 AREBBI n ṣṣbar d ufewwej ad awem iwc maḥend ad tḥesbem ijj wenneɣni ɣares řqimet d ict di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt Rum. 12:16; 1 Kur. 1:10; Fil. 2:2; 3:16; 1 Bṭ. 3:8. \x*  
\v 6 ḥima s ijj n array d ict n tmijja ad tessɛuǧam AREBBI, Babas n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\m
\v 7 S uyenni qebřem ijjen wenneɣni u ṣebrem ijjen ak-d wenneɣni, am mammec d aneɣ iqbeř Lmasiḥ ɛawed i uɛuǧi n AREBBI.  
\v 8 Maɣar ad awem iniɣ, aqa Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ idweř d amsexxar n wextan di ṭṭweɛ n tidett n AREBBI, ḥima ad iḍmen lwuɛud \add i iwaɛd AREBBI\add* i řejdud,  
\v 9 u ḥima řegnus ad ssemɣaren di AREBBI x ssibbet n arreḥmet i xasen dd-tusa am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “S uyenni ad Cek cekkareɣ jar řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt uca ad ṣebbḥeɣ Isem nnec.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:9 \xt 2 Ṣm. 22:50; Izhd. 18:50. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 10 Uca iqqar ɛawed:  
\b  
\m \qt “Farḥem, \+tl a\+tl* kenniw řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt \+tl jmiɛ\+tl* ak-d řgens nnes.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:10 \xt Aɛwd. 32:43. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 11 Uca inna ɛawed:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ḥemdem SIDI, \+tl a\+tl* marra řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt ṣebbḥem t, \+tl a\+tl* marra ccuɛub!”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:11 \xt Izhd. 117:1. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 12 Ɛawed Icaɛya iqqar:  
\b  
\m \qt “Ad yiři weẓwar n Yassa,\qt*  
\m \qt u Wenni dd-ikkaren\qt*  
\m \qt ad yiři d Azeǧif x řegnus,\qt*  
\m \qt ad dayes yiři usitem n řegnus.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt Ica. 11:10; Asa. 5:5; 22:16. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 13 AREBBI n usitem ad kenniw iccur s řefraḥet d řehna di l’iman, ḥima ad tfeyyḍem s usitem nnes zi jjehd n Arruḥ Iqeddsen.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Bulus d amsexxar n Lmasiḥ i marra řegnus  
\m
\v 14 Necc simant inu ttwasqenɛeɣ zi jjihet nwem, \add a\add* aytma, aqa kenniw tɛemmarem s tcuni, teccurem s marra tussna, ḥima ad tessřemdem ɛawed inneɣni.  
\v 15 Maca zeg uɣezdis aqa uriɣ awem s teryast, \add a\add* aytma, maḥend ad kenniw ssɛeqřeɣ, s arḍa i d ayi immewcen zi AREBBI,  
\v 16 ḥima ad iřiɣ d amsexxar n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ i řegnus, umi ttsexxareɣ i L’Injil n AREBBI, ḥima ad tiři tɣarṣt n řegnus d tameqbuč, tᵉttwaqeddes s Arruḥ Iqeddsen.  
\v 17 S uyenni ssemɣareɣ di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ zzat i AREBBI.  
\v 18 Minzi war zeɛmeɣ ad ssiwřeɣ deg imezzuɣen n řegnus x ca war zzayi t iggi Lmasiḥ s wawař d řxedmet.  
\v 19 S jjehd n řeɛřamat d řeɛjayeb uca s jjehd n Arruḥ n AREBBI, aqa tuɣa ggureɣ ttenḍeɣ zi Urcalim ař Illirikun uca kemmřeɣ \add abarreḥ n\add* Řexbar Aṣebḥan n Lmasiḥ.  
\v 20 Di \add marra\add* man aya tuɣa arezzuɣ ad barrḥeɣ s Řexbar Aṣebḥan, war iǧi mani ittwařaɣa x Yisem n Lmasiḥ \add qbeř\add*, ḥima war benniɣ x dsas n wenneɣni,  
\v 21 maca am mammec tura:  
\b  
\m \qt “Inni war zzayes ittwabarrḥen ad t ẓaren,\qt*  
\m \qt u yinni war \+tl xas\+tl* isřin, ad amnen.”\qt* \x ◘ \xo 15:21 \xt Ica. 52:15. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 22 S uyenni tuɣa war iwiḍeɣ aṭṭas n imuren, maḥend ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:22 \xt Rum. 1:13; 1 Ts. 2:18. \x*  
\v 23 Maca řexxu war ɣari bu ttasiɛ ḥima ad beccareɣ ɛad di jjwayeh-a u tuɣa ɛawed xseɣ ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ aṭṭas n iseggʷusa zeg wami. \x ◘ \xo 15:23 \xt Rum. 1:10; 15:32; 1 Ts. 3:10; 2 Tim. 1:4. \x*  
\v 24 Xmi ɣa raḥeɣ ɣar Seppanya, ssitimeɣ ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ, ad kenniw ẓareɣ, u ad zzaywem ttwassqebbḍeɣ ɣar dinni, awarni řami i ɣa arreɣ meẓri cwayt umi i ɣa ẓriɣ kenniw.   
\m
\v 25 Maca řexxu aqa ruḥeɣ ɣar Urcalim, ḥima ad sexxareɣ i imqeddasen. \x ◘ \xo 15:25 \xt Řex. 19:21; 24:17. \x*  
\v 26 Minzi tuɣa yarḍa i yinni iǧan di Makiduniya d Axaya ad ggen ca n twiza i imqeddasen imezřaḍ nni iǧan di Urcalim.  
\v 27 Tuɣa arḍan x man aya, maca tuɣa t ɛawed daysen d amarwas. Minzi mařa tuɣa \add řegnus\add* carcen di min ɣarsen d agřa x řeḥsab n Arruḥ, aqa-t ɛawed d amarwas di řegnus maḥend ad ten sexxaren s min ɣarsen d agřa x řeḥsab ddat.  
\v 28 Xmi ɣa kemmřeɣ \add tasexxart-a\add* uca ad asen ssiwḍeɣ řɣiǧet \add n twiza-ya\add* s řaman, ad dd xawem kkeɣ d abrid xmi ɣa raḥeɣ ɣar Seppanya.  
\v 29 Maca ssneɣ belli, mařa usiɣ-dd ɣarwem, ad dd-aseɣ s řmud iccuren s lbaraka n L’Injil n Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt Rum. 1:11. \x*   
\m
\v 30 Ttareɣ zzaywem, \add a\add* aytma, s Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ uca s tayri n Arruḥ, ad tbeddem nican akidi di tẓaǧit ɣar AREBBI x ssibbet inu, \x ◘ \xo 15:30 \xt 2 Kur. 1:11. \x*  
\v 31 ḥima ad ttwafekkeɣ zeg inni war yuminen ca di Yahudiyya, ḥima ad tiři tsexxart inu i imqeddasen di Urcalim d tameqbuč, \x ◘ \xo 15:31 \xt 2 Ts. 3:2. \x*  
\v 32 ḥima ad ɣarwem dd-aseɣ \add ccureɣ\add* s řefraḥet s array n AREBBI uca ad ɣarwem areyyḥeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 15:32 \xt Rum. 1:10; 15:23. \x*  
\v 33 AREBBI n řehna ad kiwem yiři marra idwem. Amin.   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 16
\s1 Aseǧem ɣar uneggaru  
\m
\v 1 Wekkřeɣ awem učmatneɣ Fubi, tenni d tamsexxart n tmesmunt di Kinxriyus,  
\v 2 ḥima ad zzayes tareḥḥbem di Siditneɣ, am mammec ittřiq i imqeddasen, uca ad tt tɛawnem di marra min zzaywem tᵉttar nettat, minzi aqa tɛawen aṭṭas, uřa řa d necc.   
\m
\v 3 Seǧmem s řehna x Priskilla d Akwila, inni d imsexxaren akidi di Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt Řex. 18:2, 26. \x*  
\v 4 Nitni sebbřen tudart nsen x ssibbet inu. War ǧiɣ d necc waha wenni ten ittqadan, maca ɛawed marra timesmunin n řegnus.   
\m
\v 5 Seǧmem ɛawed s řehna x tmesmunt tenni di taddart nsen.  
\m Seǧmem x Ibanitus, amɛizz inu, s řehna. Netta d \add ṣṣabet\add* tamezwarut n Axaya di Lmasiḥ.   
\m
\v 6 Seǧmem x Mariya s řehna. Netta tuɣa tᵉttamar aṭṭas xawem.   
\m
\v 7 Seǧmem s řehna x Andrunikus d Yuniyas inni d raǧ inu d imeḥbas akidi, aqa aten d iryazen ittwassnen ɣar rrusul, tuɣa aten di Lmasiḥ qbeř xafi.   
\m
\v 8 Seǧmem s řehna x Ampliyas, amɛizz inu di Siditneɣ.   
\m
\v 9 Seǧmem s řehna x Urbanus, wenni d amsexxar akidneɣ di Lmasiḥ,  
\m u x Astaxis amɛizz inu.   
\m
\v 10 Seǧmem s řehna x Apillis wenni ittwafarzen di Siditneɣ.  
\m Seǧmem s řehna x aytbab n taddart n Aristubulus.   
\m
\v 11 Seǧmem s řehna x Hirudiyun wenni d řaǧ inu.  
\m Seǧmem s řehna x aytbab n taddart n Narkissus inni iǧan di Siditneɣ.  
\v 12 Seǧmem s řehna x Tarifina d Tarifusa, tinni ittamaren di Siditneɣ.  
\m Seǧmem s řehna x Parsis, amɛizz inu, wenni ittamaren aṭṭas di Siditneɣ.   
\m
\v 13 Seǧmem s řehna x Rufus wenni ittwafarzen di Siditneɣ, uřa x yemmas tenni \add ɛawed am yict n yemma\add* i necc.   
\m
\v 14 Seǧmem s řehna x Asinkritus, Fligun, Hirmas, Batrubas, Hirmis uca x wawmaten inni akidsen.   
\m
\v 15 Seǧmem s řehna x Filuluɣus d Juliya d Niriyus d učmas, d Ulimbas d marra imqeddasen inni akidsen.   
\m
\v 16 Seǧmem x wayawya s usudem iqeddsen.  
\m Marra timesmunin n Lmasiḥ marra ttseǧament xawem. \x ◘ \xo 16:16 \xt 1 Kur. 16:20; 2 Kur. 13:12; 1 Ts. 5:26; 1 Bṭ. 5:14. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 17 Maca ttzawageɣ \add kenniw, a\add* aytma, maḥend ad teḥḍam zi wi itteggen amsebḍi d tɛinkrifin, barra i tɣuri i teɣrim. Beɛɛdem xasen. \x ◘ \xo 16:17 \xt Mt. 18:17; Kul. 2:8; 2 Ts. 3:6; 2 Tim. 3:5; Tit. 3:10; 2 Yḥ. 10. \x*  
\v 18 Minzi am yina war sexxaren ca i Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, maca i uɛeddis nsen. S řehrud iṣebḥen d wawařen izewwqen xeddɛen uřawen n iḥafiyyen. \x ◘ \xo 16:18 \xt Ḥiz. 13:18; Fil. 3:19. \x*  
\v 19 Minzi ṭṭaɛet nwem tᵉttwassen ɣar marra \add iwdan\add*. S uyenni farḥeɣ zzaywem, maca xseɣ ad tiřim d imiɣisen di tcuni uřa d imezdagen zi řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 16:19 \xt Mt. 10:16; 1 Kur. 14:20. \x*  
\v 20 AREBBI n řehna ad iteḥḥa cciṭan sadu iḍaren nwem deɣya. Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad kiwem yiři. Amin.   
\b  
\m
\v 21 Timutiyu, wenni d amsexxar akidi, ittseǧam-dd xawem s řehna,  
\m uřa d inni zi řaǧ inu: Lukiyus d Yasun d Susipatrus. \x ◘ \xo 16:21 \xt Řex. 13;1; 16:1; 17:5; 20:4; Fil. 2:19; Kul. 1:1; 1 Ts. 3:2; 1 Tim. 1:2. \x*   
\m
\v 22 Necc, Tartiyus, wenni yuran tabrat-a, ttseǧameɣ xawem di Siditneɣ s řehna.   
\m
\v 23 Ittseǧam-dd xawem Xayus s řehna. Netta yareḥḥeb zzayi uřa zi tmesmunt marra.  
\m Ttseǧamen-dd xawem Irastus, wenni x ssenduq n tendint, d Kwartus, tawmat. \x ◘ \xo 16:23 \xt Řex. 19:22; 2 Tim. 4:20. \x*   
\b  
\m
\v 24 I Wenni ɣar teǧa ṣṣulṭa maḥend ad kenniw iḍmen ɛlaḥsab L’Injil inu - \add L’Injil\add* i ittwabarrḥen zi jjihet n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ɛlaḥsab asargab n ssirr nni tuɣa innufaren di zzmanat \add n zic\add*,  
\v 25 maca aqa ittwasseḍhar-dd řexxu s Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* \add s ufus\add* n inabiyyen, uca ittwasscen i marra řegnus ɛlaḥsab řumur n AREBBI, wenni iǧan i řebda, ařami \add d as\add* ɣa ṭṭaɛen \add řegnus\add* s l’iman - \x ◘ \xo 16:25 \xt Afa. 1:9; 3:9, 20; Kul. 1:26; 2 Tim. 1:10; Tit. 1:2; 1 Bṭ. 1:20. \x*  
\v 26 aqa i Netta wenni d Bab n tiɣit weḥḥdes, i Netta umi ɣa yiři uɛuǧi s Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ i řebda qaɛ. Amin.   
\b  
\m
\v 27 Arḍa n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ ad kiwem yiři marra. Amin.   